C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dutchsspirits.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20modern%20distillery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20named%20after%20Shultz%20himself%2C%20runs%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20was%20like%20I%20was%20carrying%20on%20the%20plans%20when%20the%20site%20was%20built%20back%20in%20'32%20or%20'31%2C%26quot%3B%20Schlein%20said.%20%26quot%3BHad%20Prohibition%20ended%20two%20years%20sooner%2C%20Dutch's%20Spirits%20might%20have%20still%20been%20around%2C%20and%20then%20it%20would%20be%20the%20fully%20functioning%20legal%20distillery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESchlein's%20distillery%20produced%20sugar-wash%20moonshine%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20like%20vodka%2C%20he%20said.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224779%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20farmhouse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c266c6101bd0001929d260%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223138%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dutch%20gable-style%20barn%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20old%20bunkers%20and%20tunnels.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Houlihan%20Lawrence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20its%20height%2C%20when%20we%20were%20really%20pushing%20through%20with%20distribution%2C%20we%20had%20about%2030%20employees%20between%20the%20site%20and%20out%20in%20the%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20Schlein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20like%20its%20predecessor%2C%20the%20modern%20distillery%20was%20in%20the%20business%20of%20selling%20sugar-wash%20moonshine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20what%20Dutch%20Schultz%20was%20making%20on%20the%20site%20in%201932%20when%20it%20was%20raided%2C%26quot%3B%20Schlein%20said.%20Unlike%20most%20moonshine%2C%20which%20is%20generally%20made%20with%20corn%20or%20wheat%2C%20Schlein%20said%20his%20was%20made%20using%20raw%20Demerara%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20distilled%20like%20a%20vodka%2C%20so%20it's%20essentially%20a%20brown-sugar%20vodka%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20result%20is%20a%20much%20sweeter%2C%20more%20neutral%2C%20clean%20spirit%20than%20what%20is%20typically%20associated%20with%20moonshine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Schlein%20said%20he%20went%20down%20that%20path%20because%20he%20%26quot%3Breally%20wanted%20to%20pay%20a%20homage%20back%20to%20what%20was%20actually%20being%20distilled%20on%20the%20site%26quot%3B%20back%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThough%20he%20didn't%20have%20a%20background%20in%20alcohol%20production%2C%20Schlein%20couldn't%20help%20but%20be%20drawn%20into%20the%20history%20of%20the%20land.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224793%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bar%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c266c9101bd0001929d263%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223129%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bar%20and%20moonshine%20tasting%20area.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Houlihan%20Lawrence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20and%20tunnels%20were%20in%20%26quot%3Bpoor%2C%20poor%20shape%26quot%3B%20when%20Schlein%20got%20involved%20in%20the%20project%2C%20he%20said.%20But%20despite%20that%20%E2%80%94%20and%20despite%20the%20fact%20he%20said%20he%20had%20no%20background%20in%20alcohol%20production%20%E2%80%94%20he%20couldn't%20help%20but%20be%20captivated%20by%20legendary%20origins%20of%20Harvest%20Homestead%20and%20want%20to%20%26quot%3Bcarry%20on%20the%20legacy%26quot%3B%20and%20Dutch%20Schutlz's%20%26quot%3Bunfinished%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20constructed%20Harvest%20Homestead%20buildings%2C%20which%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20underground%20tunnels%20and%20bunkers%2C%20come%20with%20a%20state-of-the-art-distillery%2C%20commercial%20kitchen%2C%20and%20a%20tasting%20room%2C%20which%20Schlein%20used%20to%20welcome%20visitors%20and%20run%20tours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20modern%20touches%20Schlein%20added%20include%20a%20set%20of%20solar%20panels%20on%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20main%20barn%20and%20another%20set%20on%20a%20smaller%20building%20on%20the%20land%2C%20which%20he%20said%20provide%20%26quot%3Bmore%20or%20less%20enough%20%5Benergy%5D%20to%20feed%20the%20electrical%20needs%20of%20the%20site.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENods%20to%20the%20past%20are%20sprinkled%20around%20the%20property%2C%20including%20a%20portrait%20of%20Schultz%20in%20the%20tasting%20room.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224743%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrance.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c266b7101bd0001929d24e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223162%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20portrait%20of%20Dutch%20Schultz%20hangs%20on%20the%20property.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Houlihan%20Lawrence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20renovations%20were%20completed%2C%20Schlein%20said%20he%20opened%20up%20the%20property%20to%20the%20public%20in%20various%20ways.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20used%20for%20tours%2C%20tastings%2C%20events.%20It's%20been%20used%20as%20a%20blending%20and%20bottling%20facility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20weddings%20there%2C%20birthdays%20there%2C%20concerts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20a%20very%20special%20place%20that%20kind%20of%20lends%20itself%20to%20being%20experienced%2C%26quot%3B%20Schlein%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20at%20its%20finest%20when%20people%20are%20there%20to%20rediscover%20it%20for%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20of%20Schlein's%20favorite%20spots%20is%20a%20balcony%20off%20one%20of%20the%20parlors%20that%20provides%20sweeping%20views%20of%20the%20surrounding%20countryside.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224743%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Weddings%20have%20been%20held%20at%20Harvest%20Homestead.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c26689101bd0001929d209%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223162%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWeddings%20have%20been%20held%20at%20Harvest%20Homestead.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Houlihan%20Lawrence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20sitting%20out%20there%20when%20the%20sun%20goes%20down%2C%20it's%20absolutely%20picturesque%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pretty%20special%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20it%20is%20close%20to%20the%20Pine%20Plains%20village%2C%20the%20property%20is%20private%20and%20well%20concealed%20from%20nearby%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Gates%2C%20the%20Houlihan%20Lawrence%20listing%20agent%20for%20the%20property%2C%20echoed%20Schlein's%20sentiments.%20Speaking%20to%20Insider%2C%20Gates%20said%20its%20setting%20on%20the%20Shekomeko%20Creek%20also%20makes%20it%20unique.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20Gates%20said%20the%20property%20has%20already%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20already%20had%20one%20significant%20person%20from%20the%20hospitality%20space%20look%20at%20it%20and%20another%20person%20who's%20coming%20in%20August%20who's%20a%20significant%20person%20in%20the%20world%20of%20distillery%20and%20whiskey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20pretty%20excited.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20while%20Schlein%20is%20proud%20that%20he%20brought%20Harvest%20Homestead%20back%20to%20life%2C%20he%20said%20he's%20ready%20for%20a%20new%20owner%20to%20continue%20Schultz's%20legacy.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20surrounding%20land.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c266a8101bd0001929d229%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20property%20sits%20on%20over%20340-acres%20of%20pristine%20farmland.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Houlihan%20Lawrence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESchlein%20describes%20himself%20as%20more%20of%20a%20developer%20than%20someone%20suited%20to%20run%20the%20operational%20side%20of%20a%20commercial%20moonshine-making%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20confident%20as%20I%20am%20in%20my%20vision%20and%20in%20my%20kind%20of%20execution%20of%20the%20building%20and%20the%20development%20of%20the%20site%20as%20it%20stands%20now%2C%20I%20know%20my%20limitations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Schlein%20sees%20it%2C%20a%20new%20owner%20could%20come%20in%20and%20make%20Harvest%20Homestead%20run%20the%20way%20he%20said%20it%20should%20be%20run%2C%20either%20as%20a%20farm%20housing%20animals%2C%20a%20private%20property%2C%20or%20to%20distill%20moonshine%20as%20he%20has%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20build%20a%20car%2C%20but%20I'm%20probably%20not%20the%20best%20driver%2C%20let's%20put%20it%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Schlein%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-barn-distillery-prohibition-era-hidden-treasure-sale-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690628580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c268e29440b70019271613%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-barn-distillery-prohibition-era-hidden-treasure-sale-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Owner%20Ariel%20Shlein%20said%20the%20farm%20is%20built%20on%20top%20of%20the%20remnants%20of%20a%20bootlegging%20operation%20once%20run%20by%20infamous%20mobster%20Dutch%20Schultz.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mnoyen%40insider.com%20(Maria%20Noyen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-barn-distillery-prohibition-era-hidden-treasure-sale-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Venom%203%20gets%20a%202024%20release%20date%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690628319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2