s%20received%20dozens%20of%20High%20Mobility%20Artillery%20Rocket%20Systems%20or%20HIMARS%2C%20which%20have%20been%20crucial%20in%20its%20defensive%20and%20offensive%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US-made%20system%20is%20an%20advanced%20missile%20launcher%20that%20is%20mounted%20on%20a%20truck%20and%20can%20fire%20six%2C%20GPS-guided%20missiles%20that%20can%20reach%20up%20to%2050%20miles%20(80%20km).%20Its%20reach%20allows%20Ukraine%20to%20destroy%20high-value%20targets%20that%20are%20far%20behind%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20missiles%20are%20also%20fixed%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20truck%2C%20the%20system%20is%20also%20flexible%20and%20can%20adapt%20to%20changing%20war%20tactics%2C%20Ben%20Caves%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20leader%20at%20the%20RAND%20Corporation%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20important%20characteristic%20with%20the%20HIMARS%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20can%20be%20moved%20really%20quickly%20so%20that%20the%20Russians%20can%20never%20identify%20where%20they%20were%2C%20so%20that%20has%20been%20extremely%20useful%20for%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20Caves%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20hurt%20the%20Russian%20logistical%20effort%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20meant%20the%20Russians%20have%20had%20to%20push%20stuff%20more%20to%20the%20rear%2C%20and%20that's%20made%20Russia%20in%20turn%2C%20more%20vulnerable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weapon%20was%20particularly%20useful%20to%20Ukrainian%20forces%20last%20November%20when%20they%20successfully%20pushed%20Russian%20forces%20away%20from%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Kherson%2C%20which%20it%20was%20occupying%20at%20the%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fzelenskiy.official%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0XNDe7mJAktTGa5GqhkmnqMPnmcPAMTN4nUhJ6i7Yq5HrsnWwhpCw7Ba2a4Y4qa5wl%5C%22%3Epreviously%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20system%20is%20vital%20to%20his%20country's%20efforts.%20%26quot%3BHIMARS%20and%20other%20precision%20weapons%20are%20turning%20the%20course%20of%20the%20war%20in%20our%20favor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPatriot%20Missile%20Systems%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223471%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22patrioto%20missile%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bfd6bfed4f460019630670%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222603%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Army%20MIM-104%20Patriot%2C%20a%20surface-to-air%20missile%20system%20launcher%2C%20is%20pictured%20at%20Rzeszow-Jasionka%20airport%2C%20Poland%2C%20on%20March%2016%2C%202022%3Cp%3EFabrizio%20Bensch%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US-provided%20systems%20arrived%20in%20Ukraine%20in%20April%2C%20with%20Defense%20Minister%20Oleksii%20Reznikov%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Foleksiireznikov%2Fstatus%2F1648627423636799488%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22195438bb8565851e44f17340c51b421a%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2260%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Foleksiireznikov%2Fstatus%2F1648627423636799488%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweeting%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20our%20beautiful%20Ukrainian%20sky%20becomes%20more%20secure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Patriot%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sophisticated%20air%20defense%20systems%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20stop%20cruise%20missiles%20and%20short-range%20ballistic%20missiles%20before%20they%20reach%20their%20target.%20It%20can%20also%20shoot%20down%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20anti-air%20system%20has%20bolstered%20the%20military's%20air%20defenses%2C%20which%20have%20previously%20been%20unable%20to%20intercept%20more%20modern%20Russian%20missiles%2C%20Dr.%20Huseyn%20Aliyev%2C%20from%20the%20Research%20Center%20for%20East%20European%20Studies%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPatriots%20are%20only%20a%20recent%20addition%20to%20Ukraine's%20army%2C%20but%20they%20have%20already%20had%20a%20very%20notable%20effect%20on%20their%20ability%20to%20shoot%20down%2C%20for%20example%2C%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20which%20they%20couldn't%20really%20shoot%20down%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20could%20only%20target%20Cruise%20missiles%2C%20but%20now%20they%20can%20bring%20down%20even%20the%20most%20advanced%20Russian%20so-called%20hypersonic%20missiles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Ukrainian%20officials%20claimed%20they%20used%20a%20Patriot%C2%A0to%C2%A0shoot%20down%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-success-with-us-patriot-missiles-stunned-the-pentagon-analyst-2023-5%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Eseveral%C2%A0Russian%20hypersonic%20Kinzhal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0missiles%2C%20which%20Moscow%20previously%20boasted%20were%20unstoppable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EJavelin%20anti-tank%20missile%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221778%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20use%20a%20launcher%20with%20US%20Javelin%20missiles.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3a04a048ff200190c8ba1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20this%20image%20released%20by%20Ukrainian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%2C%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20use%20a%20launcher%20with%20US%20Javelin%20missiles.%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20American-made%2C%20FGM-148%20anti-tank%20missile%20is%20commonly%20known%20as%20a%20Javelin%2C%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20have%20given%20it%20a%20new%20name%3A%20%26quot%3BSaint%20Javelin%2C%20Protector%20of%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.militarytimes.com%2Foff-duty%2Fgearscout%2F2022%2F05%2F12%2Fjavelin-missile-made-by-the-us-wielded-by-ukraine-feared-by-russia%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Military%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portable%20surface-to-air%20missile%2C%20which%20can%20be%20fired%20from%20the%20shoulder%20or%20from%20a%20launcher%2C%20is%20highly%20effective%20against%20main%20battle%20tanks%20and%20other%20armored%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20summer%2C%20the%20US%20government%20provided%20Ukraine%20with%20more%20than%205%2C000%20Javelins%20as%20part%20of%20its%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2022%2F08%2F05%2Fukraine-war-javelins-russia-tanks%2F%5C%22%3E%248%20billion%20military%20aid%20package.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaves%20told%20Insider%20that%20Javelins%20were%20particularly%20effective%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20the%20war%20when%20Russia%20failed%20to%20take%20Kyiv.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20great%20in%20taking%20out%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20Russian%20armor%2C%26quot%3B%20Cave%20told%20Insider.%26quot%3BBut%20that%20was%20probably%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20tactics%20that%20the%20Russians%20employed%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20they%20made%20themselves%20easy%20targets%20and%20underestimated%20the%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20also%20in%20possession%20of%20UK-made%20Next%20Generation%20Light%20Anti-tank%20Weapon%20(NLAW)%20which%20Caves%20said%20is%20equally%20as%20useful%20because%20it's%20smaller%20and%20requires%20very%20little%20training.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20give%20these%20weapons%20to%20someone%20and%20they%20can%20easily%20use%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStorm%20Shadow%20Missiles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221778%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Storm%20Shadow%20cruise%20missile%20on%20display%20outdoors%20on%20a%20plinth%20during%20the%20Paris%20Air%20Show%20in%20Le%20Bourget%2C%20north%20of%20Paris%2C%20France%2C%20Monday%2C%20June%2019%2C%202023%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3a060cf07780019661ca1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Storm%20Shadow%20cruise%20missile%20is%20on%20display%20during%20the%20Paris%20Air%20Show%20in%20Le%20Bourget%2C%20north%20of%20Paris%2C%20France%2C%20Monday%2C%20June%2019%2C%202023%3Cp%3ELewis%20Joly%2FAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Storm%20Shadow%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20SCALP%2C%20has%20been%20described%20as%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20Ukraine's%20counteroffensive%2C%20given%20its%20evasive%20abilities%2C%20precise%20targeting%2C%20and%20its%20155-mile%20range.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20missiles%2C%20which%20were%20recently%20provided%20by%20the%20UK%2C%20are%20designed%20to%20fly%20low%20after%20launch%20to%20evade%20detection%20and%20have%20an%20onboard%20infrared%20target-seeking%20system%20that%20allows%20them%20to%20recognize%20planned%20targets%20for%20a%20precision%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarina%20Miron%2C%20a%20post-doctoral%20researcher%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20War%20Studies%20at%20King's%20College%20London%2C%20told%20Insider%C2%A0%20that%20Storm%20Shadows%20%26quot%3Bact%20as%20a%20force%20multiplier%20for%20the%20Ukrainian%20forces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20longest-range%20missiles%20that%20the%20Ukrainians%20can%20fire%20from%20their%20Soviet%20fighter%20jets%20to%20strike%20high-value%20targets%20far%20behind%20the%20enemy%20lines%20such%20as%20command%20and%20control%20centers%2C%20logistical%20nods%2C%20ammunition%20depots%2C%20and%20other%20hardened%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20in%20turn%20helps%20to%20disrupt%20operations%20and%20reduce%20the%20military%20capacity%20of%20the%20Russian%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20these%20missiles%20are%20few%2C%20they%20are%20still%20important%20to%20give%20Ukraine%20the%20ability%20to%20strike%20and%20destroy%20such%20targets%20without%20a%20major%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBradley%20Fighting%20Vehicles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221778%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Bradley%20Infantry%20Fighting%20Vehicle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3a7e4048ff200190c9425%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20group%20of%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Bradley%20Infantry%20Fighting%20Vehicle%2C%20seemingly%20taken%20before%20it%20was%20damaged.%3Cp%3EHanna%20Maliar%2FTelegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20received%20a%20major%20delivery%20of%20armored%20fighting%20vehicles%20from%20Europe%20and%20the%20US%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20US-provided%20M2%20Bradley%20fighting%20vehicles%20have%20proven%20particularly%20successful%2C%20according%20to%20Aliyev.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20important%20because%20they%20help%20Ukraine%20to%20move%20infantry%20to%20the%20frontlines%2C%26quot%3B%20Alivey%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20only%20offer%20protection%20to%20the%20military%20personnel%20but%20also%20allow%20for%20flexibility%20so%20that%20soldiers%20can%20adapt%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20armored%20vehicle%20like%20the%20Bradley%20pairs%20heavy%20firepower%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20transport%20up%20to%2015%20soldiers%2C%20Alivey%20said.It%20also%20comes%20with%20night%20vision%2C%20range%20calculators%2C%20and%20fire%20control.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20purpose%20is%20actually%20not%20to%20fight%20tanks%20or%20not%20to%20fight%20on%20the%20battle%2C%20but%20just%20to%20move%20infantry%2C%20to%20offer%20protection%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20the%20most%20dangerous%20part%20for%20troops%20is%20just%20getting%20to%20the%20frontlines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOnly%20time%20will%20tell%20how%20useful%20the%20weapons%20really%20are%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20still%20unclear%20how%20Ukraine's%20counteroffensive%20will%20unfold%2C%20and%20how%20long%20the%20Western%20weapons%20will%20hold%20until%20Ukraine%20will%20need%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20top%20Ukrainian%20general%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66306150%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22d9af04ccb514653604a3b0b4a5623f98%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66306150%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20that%20because%20Russia%20has%20littered%20the%20frontlines%20in%20south%20Ukraine%20with%20multi-layered%20minefields%2C%20Western%20tanks%20are%20proving%20ineffective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20vehicles%20became%20badly%20damaged%2C%20Gen.%20Oleksandr%20Tarnavskyi%20said%2C%20forcing%20Ukrainian%20units%20to%20leave%20them%20behind%20and%20advance%20slowly%20on%20foot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20don't%20underestimate%20the%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20Tarnavskyi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeadliest-western-provided-weapons-ukraine-is-using-to-fight-russia-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690626674000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bfd168ed4f46001962fdf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeadliest-western-provided-weapons-ukraine-is-using-to-fight-russia-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine%20has%20been%20receiving%20military%20aid%20from%20the%20West%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war.%20Experts%20told%20Insider%20