20and%20lynching%20of%20Muslim%20youth%2C%20incarceration%20of%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20professors%2C%20lawyers%2C%20and%20students%2C%20and%20silencing%20of%20newspapers%20and%20journalists%20who%20dared%20to%20question%20the%20government%20policies.%20It%20was%20gradually%20a%20bare-bones%20newsroom%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20Ravish%20Kumar%20that%20was%20responding%20to%20these%20unparalleled%20daily%20developments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20film%20does%20brilliantly%20is%20to%20situate%20Kumar%2C%20his%20prime-time%20show%2C%20and%20NDTV%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20media%20ecosystem%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20particularly%20television%20news%20%E2%80%93%20that%20was%20openly%20spewing%20hatred%2C%20spreading%20misinformation%2C%20and%20goading%20crowds%20to%20take%20matters%20into%20their%20own%20hands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28171909%2FF8336CC7-9A67-4E0B-A372-FF8D82E22C16.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28171909%2FF8336CC7-9A67-4E0B-A372-FF8D82E22C16.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28171909%2FF8336CC7-9A67-4E0B-A372-FF8D82E22C16-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665668%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWhile%20We%20Watched%20screening%20in%20New%20York.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMultiple%20media%20channels%2C%20both%20Hindi%20and%20English%2C%20indulged%20in%20defining%20an%20exclusionary%20meaning%20of%20patriotism%20and%20delivered%20their%20unadulterated%20hate%20messages%20to%20millions%20of%20homes%20every%20day.%20Kumar%20completely%20rejected%20the%20dominant%20format%20of%20other%20prime-time%20anchors%20that%20relied%20on%20sensational%20and%20high-decibel%20debate%20among%20talking%20heads%20that%20allowed%20them%20to%20distribute%20hatred%20as%20news.%20The%20show%20became%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20create%20an%20alternative%20explanation%20of%20what%20was%20unfolding%20every%20day%20and%20done%20through%20his%20sheer%20power%20of%20storytelling%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20long%20monologues%20that%20tried%20to%20break%20through%20the%20fog.%20Being%20a%20very%20popular%20anchor%20on%20NDTV%20for%20multiple%20years%2C%20people%20flocked%20to%20his%20show%20to%20hear%20his%20views%20on%20the%20pressing%20issues%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShukla%20has%20mentioned%20in%20interviews%20that%20he%20liked%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20persuasive%20storytelling%20alongside%20his%20connection%20with%20the%20audience%20that%20allowed%20the%20anchor%20to%20often%20even%20chide%20them%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cjr.org%2Fthe_media_today%2Fqa_while_we_watched_documentary_india.php%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewatching%20other%20channels%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20name%20of%20news.%20But%20really%20what%20he%20ends%20up%20doing%20is%20to%20tell%20us%20a%20larger%20story%20of%20attempted%20decimation%3A%20of%20the%20news%20network%20that%20Kumar%20was%20a%20part%20of-NDTV%2C%20of%20the%20reporters%2C%20support%20staff%2C%20distribution%2C%20viewership%2C%20and%20above%20all%20what%20hurt%20Kumar%20the%20most-%20his%20audience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20giving%20away%20too%20much%20from%20the%20film%2C%20one%20can%20only%20note%20the%20poignant%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20film%20captures%20this%20gradual%20decline%20in%20the%20media%20network%20and%20Ravish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20own%20show%20then%20slowly%20creeping%20into%20his%20life%20as%20his%20family%20starts%20feeling%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20hostility%20and%20trolling%20around%20them.%20The%20film%20offers%20you%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20happens%20when%20your%20phone%20number%20is%20circulated%20in%20the%20media%20and%20you%20dare%20to%20listen%20and%20occasionally%20respond%20to%20those%20who%20abuse%20you%20with%20death%20threats%20merely%20makes%20one%20both%20horrified%20and%20truly%20terrified.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20Kumar%20often%20speaks%20back%20with%20patience%2C%20laughs%2C%20and%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20sings.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20incredulous%20moment%20that%20just%20tells%20you%20something%20about%20his%20faith%20that%20if%20only%20he%20could%20communicate%20with%20his%20audience%20more%2C%20he%20can%20maybe%20make%20a%20difference.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.v-dem.net%2Fdocuments%2F12%2Fdr_2021.pdf%5C%22%3EVarieties%20of%20Democracy%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20dataset%20from%20202%20countries%20on%20measuring%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20noted%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20share%20of%20the%20population%20under%20autocracies%20increased%20from%2048%25%20in%202010%20to%2068%25%20in%202020.%20India%20is%20among%20the%20top%2010%20on%20this%20list.%20The%20report%20noted%20that%20the%20largest%20democracy%20is%20now%20an%20%E2%80%9Celectoral%20autocracy%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20continued%20decline%20is%20mentioned%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fv-dem.net%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2023%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20far%20as%20media%20freedom%20is%20concerned%2C%20Reporters%20Without%20Borders%20(RSF)%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frsf.org%2Fen%2Findex%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0noted%20that%20India%20has%20declined%20from%20150%20to%20161%20in%20their%20world%20ranking%20and%20journalists%20continued%20to%20be%20detained%20and%20censored.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJournalist%20Siddique%20Kappan%20spent%20more%20than%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-64494426%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etwo%20years%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20jail%20for%20daring%20to%20report%20on%20the%20gangrape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20Dalit%20woman%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Hathras.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20rankings%20reflect%20general%20trends%20and%20there%20can%20be%20debates%20on%20the%20actual%20terminology%20of%20electoral%20autocracy%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20We%20Watched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20translates%20what%20these%20figures%20mean%20in%20the%20everyday%20Indian%20experience%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20lack%20of%20press%20freedom%20and%20rights%20in%20general.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20know%20how%20Ravish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20stint%20at%20NDTV%20ended%20%E2%80%93%20the%20film%20does%20not%20show%20that.%20But%20it%20shows%20%E2%80%93%20through%20different%20moments%20in%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20some%20very%20tender%20and%20some%20harsh%20%E2%80%93%20that%20he%20was%20not%20willing%20to%20fall%20in%20line%20and%20compromise%20even%20as%20the%20resources%20at%20his%20disposal%20were%20depleting%20fast%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20literally%20collapsing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20film%20also%20depicts%20how%20Kumar%20starts%20realising%20that%20a%20section%20of%20the%20audience%20that%20doted%20on%20him%20was%20slowly%20getting%20persuaded%20by%20the%20frenzy%20and%20the%20hatred%20espoused%20by%20other%20channels%20and%20the%20world%20around%20him.%20The%20film%20beautifully%20captures%20a%20deeply%20complex%20Kumar%20who%20acknowledges%20the%20changes%20that%20Indian%20society%20and%20politics%20is%20undergoing%20but%20also%20exudes%20an%20unfaltering%20faith%20in%20his%20ability%20to%20level%20with%20his%20audience.%20That%20is%20Ravish%20Kumar%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20his%20calling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJinee%20Lokaneeta%20and%20Sangay%20Mishra%20teach%20Political%20Science%20at%20Drew%20University%2C%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690624817000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28172559%2F359665950_1676607739434024_4017294775728816439_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fin-while-we-watched-ravish-kumar-is-a-picture-of-courage-in-perilous-times%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20global%20attention%20to%20the%20film%2C%20it%20has%20not%20seen%20a%20single%20commercial%20screening%20in%20India%20yet.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fin-while-we-watched-ravish-kumar-is-a-picture-of-courage-in-perilous-times%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20'exceptional'%20Roman%20shipwreck%20was%20discovered%20with%20hundreds%20of%20intact%202%2C000-year-old%20jars%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Italy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20of%20a%20pile%20Ancient%20Roman%20vases%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20Mediterranean%20sea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c4c4fdcf07780019670912%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Italian%20Carabinieri%20discovered%20the%20remains%20of%20an%20Ancient%20Roman%20cargo%20ship%20full%20of%20terracotta%20jars%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bamphorae.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECarabinieri%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERelics%20of%20an%20ancient%20Roman%20cargo%20ship%20were%20found%20near%20Rome%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20vessel%20was%20filled%20with%20hundreds%20of%20Roman%20vases%2C%20and%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20more%20than%2020%20meters%20long.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20local%20police%20authority%20called%20the%20discovery%20%26quot%3Bexceptional.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wreck%20of%20a%202%2C000-year-old%20Roman%20cargo%20ship%20was%20found%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Italy%20on%20Friday%20in%20what%20archaeologists%20have%20described%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%26quot%3B%20discovery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vessel%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20second%20or%20first%20century%20BC%2C%20was%20found%20loaded%20with%20hundreds%20of%20ancient%20Roman%20terracotta%20jars%2C%20also%20known%20as%20amphorae.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EItalian%20news%20organization%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Froma.repubblica.it%2Fcronaca%2F2023%2F07%2F28%2Fnews%2Fcivitavecchia_scoperto_il_relitto_di_unantica_nave_romana_del_ii_secolo_avanti_cristo-409264150%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELa%20Repubblica%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20the%20ship%20could%20have%20arrived%20from%20Spain%2C%20carrying%20a%20cargo%20of%20olives%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20wine%2C%20peaches%2C%20and%20figs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cultural-heritage%20division%20of%20the%20Carabinieri%20police%20found%20the%20wreck%20near%20the%20town%20of%20Civitavecchia%2C%20about%2050%20miles%20north%20of%20Italy's%20capital%20city%2C%20in%20a%20sandy%20seabed%20about%20160%20meters%20(525%20feet)%20deep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Carabinieri%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20exceptional%20discovery%20represents%20an%20important%20example%20of%20the%20sinking%20of%20a%20Roman%20ship%20which%20faced%20the%20perils%20of%20the%20sea%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20reach%20the%20coast%2C%20and%20bears%20witness%20to%20the%20ancient%20maritime%20trade%20routes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20local%20authorities%20were%20taking%20all%20necessary%20steps%20to%20safeguard%20and%20protect%20the%20archaeological%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ship%20was%20likely%20part%20of%20the%20Cura%20Annonae%2C%20an%20ancient%20Roman%20body%20that%20was%20charged%20with%20importing%20and%20distributing%20grain%20to%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20cities%20of%20Rome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EItaly's%20Mediterranean%20coastline%20is%20dotted%20with%20Roman%20shipwrecks.%20Last%20year%2C%20archaeologists%20discovered%20a%20similar%20shipwreck%20dating%20back%20nearly%202%2C200%20years%20stocked%20with%20jars%20used%20to%20transport%20food%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Palermo%2C%20Sicily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-roman-cargo-ship-food-jars-was-near-the-coast-of-italy-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690624466000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c4c50a048ff200190d7813%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-roman-cargo-ship-food-jars-was-near-the-coast-of-italy-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20vessel%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20second%20or%20first%20century%20BC%2C%20was%20found%20loaded%20with%20hundreds%20of%20ancient%20Roman%20terracotta%20jars%2C%20also%20known%20as%20amphorae.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mbiino%40insider.com%20(Marta%20Biino)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancient-roman-cargo-ship-food-jars-was-near-the-coast-of-italy-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NEP%20will%20give%20due%20respect%2C%20credit%20to%20every%20Indian%20language%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690624424000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F28%2Ffull%2F1690529694-8521.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus