tle%22%3A%22The%20music%20industry%20is%20now%20driven%20by%20data%2C%20but%20this%20CEO%20still%20makes%20decisions%20based%20on%20'gut%20feel%20and%20instinct'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225632%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Gudinski%20is%20CEO%20of%20the%20Mushroom%20Group.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c39ab1048ff200190c8663%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224224%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatt%20Gudinski%20is%20CEO%20of%20the%20Mushroom%20Group.%3Cp%3EMushroom%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMushroom%20Records%20was%20founded%20in%20Australia%20in%20the%201970s%20by%20Michael%20Gudinski.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHis%20son%20Matt%20joined%20the%20company%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017%20and%20became%20CEO%20when%20his%20father%20died%20in%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMatt%20Gudinski%20says%20Mushroom%20helps%20artists%20build%20long-term%20careers%20and%20gives%20them%20creative%20control.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20if%20you%20wanted%20to%20listen%20to%20a%20particular%20artist%2C%20you%20needed%20to%20drive%20to%20a%20record%20store%20and%20buy%20their%20album%20or%20CD.%20And%20for%20many%20years%2C%20buying%20that%20album%20usually%20cost%20considerably%20more%20than%20seeing%20that%20performer%20play%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%20and%20streaming%20platforms%20like%20Spotify%20changed%20all%20that%2C%20putting%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20tracks%20in%20your%20pocket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20also%20meant%20that%20most%20artists%20now%20make%20far%20less%20from%20releasing%20music%2C%20which%20is%20partly%20why%20the%20cost%20of%20seeing%20them%20play%20live%20has%20soared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20stopped%20many%20fans%20of%20megastars%20artists%20such%20as%20Beyonce%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20shelling%20out%20hundreds%20%E2%80%93%20or%20even%20thousands%20%E2%80%93%20of%20dollars%20to%20see%20their%20id