6quot%3B%20model%20%E2%80%93%20where%20one%20company%20has%20a%20deal%20that%20encompasses%20both%20an%20act's%20recorded%20music%20as%20well%20as%20their%20tours%20and%20other%20aspects%20such%20as%20merchandise%20and%20using%20their%20music%20in%20films%2C%20TV%20or%20adverts.%20(Madonna%20signed%20a%2010-year%20%26quot%3B360%26quot%3B%20deal%20with%20Live%20Nation%20worth%20a%20reported%20%24120%20million%20in%202007.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222934%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kylie%20Minogue%20performing%20at%20a%20WorldPride%20concert%20in%20Sydney%20in%20February.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c2ff2e048ff200190c624f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKylie%20Minogue%20started%20her%20recording%20career%20on%20Mushroom%20Records.%3Cp%3EDon%20Arnold%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMushroom%20is%20celebrating%20its%2050th%20anniversary%20and%20Gudinski%20says%20the%20approaches%20taken%20by%20his%20father%20Michael%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20company%20in%20the%201970s%20and%20ran%20it%20until%20his%20untimely%20death%20aged%2068%20in%20March%202021%2C%20helped%20it%20survive%20and%20prosper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Gudinski%20was%20such%20a%20towering%20figure%20in%20Australian%20music%20that%20the%20Victorian%20government%20held%20a%20state%20memorial%20in%20his%20honour%2C%20with%20performances%20and%20messages%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20Minogue%2C%20Sheeran%2C%20Sting%20and%20Bruce%20Springsteen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMushroom%20released%20Minogue's%20debut%20album%20and%20she%20thanked%20the%20entrepreneur%20for%20taking%20a%20%26quot%3Bscrawny%20girl%20from%20Melbourne%20to%20the%20world%20and%20back%20home%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2021-03-24%2Fmichael-gudinski-state-memorial-ed-sheeran%2F100026270%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EABC%20News%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Gudinski%2C%20now%2038%2C%20joined%20Mushroom%20when%20he%20was%2017%20and%20says%20he%20worked%20alongside%20his%20dad%20for%20the%20past%20decade.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20reservations%20about%20taking%20the%20reins%20and%20building%20upon%20the%20foundations%20my%20father%20laid%20and%20the%20amazing%20legacy%20he%20built%2C%20but%20was%20determined%20to%20do%20it%20my%20own%20way.%20We%20worked%20so%20well%20together%20for%20many%20years%20as%20we%20both%20had%20a%20different%20approach%20that%20complemented%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGudinski%20insists%20that%20Mushroom's%20ethos%20remains%20the%20same%20%E2%80%93%20helping%20artists%20build%20careers%20over%20the%20long%20term%2C%20not%20chasing%20overnight%20success%20and%20giving%20them%20substantial%20creative%20control.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20really%20believe%20in%20something%2C%20we%20commit%20to%20something%20and%20stay%20the%20course.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223555%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Australian%20singer-songwriter%20Vance%20Joy%20performs%20in%20Madrid%2C%20Spain%20in%20April.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3000e048ff200190c6298%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVance%20Joy%20performs%20in%20Madrid%2C%20Spain%20in%20April.%3Cp%3EMariano%20Regidor%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20decisions%20in%20the%20music%20business%20are%20now%20driven%20by%20data%2C%20%26quot%3Bgut%20feel%20and%20instinct%26quot%3B%20remain%20part%20of%20the%20equation%20for%20his%20company%20at%20least.%20Take%20that%20away%2C%20Gudinski%20says%2C%20and%20they'd%20%26quot%3Blose%20the%20essence%20of%20what%20makes%20Mushroom%20what%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20YouTube%20and%20other%20platforms%20means%20artists%20now%20have%20more%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%20to%20start%20their%20careers%20and%20get%20themselves%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20Australian%20says%20artists%20still%20benefit%20from%20being%20signed%20to%20a%20label.%20He%20likens%20the%20music%20business%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20there%20used%20to%20be%20%26quot%3B10%20opportunities%20and%20100%20artists.%20Now%20there's%201%2C000%20artists%20%E2%80%93%20but%20still%20only%2010%20opportunities.%26quot%3B%20That%20makes%20it%20%26quot%3Breally%20challenging%26quot%3B%20for%20artists%20to%20%26quot%3Bcut%20through%20and%20take%20that%20next%20step.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusic%20fans%20are%20also%20faced%20with%20an%20avalanche%20of%20choice%2C%20with%20endless%20new%20content%20competing%20with%20more%20established%20artists%20(tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20tracks%20are%20uploaded%20every%20day%20to%20platforms%20like%20Spotify.)%20As%20Gudinski%20puts%20it%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20always%20something%20else%20put%20in%20front%20of%20you%20that%20you%20discover%20you%20like.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoes%20he%20still%20listen%20to%20albums%20from%20start%20to%20finish%3F%20%26quot%3BNot%20as%20much%20as%20I%20once%20did%20%E2%80%93%20I'm%20even%20reluctant%20to%20say%20that.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStreaming%20has%20brought%20challenges%20to%20the%20industry%2C%20but%20he%20thinks%20it's%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20done%20a%20lot%20more%20good%20than%20not%26quot%3B%20by%20making%20music%20far%20more%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20proved%20lucrative%20for%20the%20big%20record%20companies%2C%20with%20Universal%20Music%20this%20week%20posting%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftools.eurolandir.com%2Ftools%2FPressreleases%2FGetPressRelease%2F%3FID%3D4357553%26lang%3Den-GB%26companycode%3Dus-umg%26v%3Ddark%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E8.7%25%20rise%20in%20revenues%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year%20to%20just%20over%205.1%20billion%20euros%2C%20for%20example.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222351%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kylie%20Minogue%20performs%20at%20the%20Mushroom%20Records%2025th%20anniversary%20concert%20in%20Melbourne%20in%20November%201998.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c30358048ff200190c6368%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221763%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKylie%20Minogue%20performs%20at%20the%20Mushroom%20Records%2025th%20anniversary%20concert%20in%20Melbourne%20in%201998.%3Cp%3EMartin%20Philbey%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20many%20artists%20not%20quite%20at%20the%20level%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%20or%20Coldplay%20are%20already%20struggling%20to%20make%20a%20living%20from%20the%20music%20business%2C%20it's%20not%20likely%20to%20get%20any%20easier%20given%20the%20potential%20impact%20of%20AI.%20Gudinski%20thinks%20the%20jury%20is%20still%20out%2C%20but%20admits%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20challenge%20many%20parts%20of%20our%20industry%3B%20whether%20that's%20for%20the%20better%20or%20the%20worse%20still%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20There's%20no%20doubt%20it's%20going%20to%20have%20a%20big%20impact.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20Mushroom's%20already%20had%20several%20pitches%20for%20live%20shows%20by%20manufactured%20characters%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bartists%20that%20are%20not%20artists.%26quot%3B%20Despite%20its%20history%20of%20being%20a%20leader%20rather%20than%20a%20follower%2C%20Gudinski%20says%20AI%20might%20be%20one%20time%20for%20the%20company%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20how%20it%20all%20shakes%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Gudinski%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3a78bcf07780019662378%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Gudinski%20founded%20Mushroom%20Records%20in%201972.%3Cp%3EMushroom%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20Mushroom%20has%20relaunched%20its%20record%20label%20in%20the%20UK%20that%20was%20once%20home%20to%20acts%20such%20as%20Garbage%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20has%20250%20staff%20working%20in%20offices%20in%20Australia%2C%20Europe%20and%20North%20America%2C%20and%20recently%20signed%20a%20global%20distribution%20deal%20with%20Universal.%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20many%20independent%20record%20labels%2C%20to%20use%20an%20old%20term%2C%20working%20with%20artists%20on%20a%20global%20front%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Gudinski%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20Mushroom%20remain%20a%20private%20company%20in%20its%20sixth%20decade%20and%20beyond%3F%20While%20a%20sale%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20part%20of%20our%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds%3A%20%26quot%3BNever%20say%20never%20%E2%80%A6%20it's%20a%20really%20challenging%20time%20for%20anybody%20%E2%80%93%20independent%2C%20major%20label%20or%20listed%20company%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20investing%20in%20new%20music.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmushroom-music-ceo-still-makes-decisions-gut-feel-and-instinct-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690623951000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c39ab1048ff200190c8663%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmushroom-music-ceo-still-makes-decisions-gut-feel-and-instinct-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Matt%20Gudinski%20started%20working%20for%20the%20Mushroom%20Group%20when%20he%20was%2017%2C%20and%20took%20over%20running%20the%20company%20when%20his%20father%20died%20two%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cjohnston%40insider.com%20(Chris%20Johnston)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmushroom-music-ceo-still-makes-decisions-gut-feel-and-instinct-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mizoram%20CM%20Decries%20UCC%