Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZoramthanga%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20response%20to%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20that%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20of%20the%20trouble%20in%20Manipur%2C%20thousands%20of%20%E2%80%A6%20Kuki%20internally%20displaced%20persons%20(IDPs)%20have%20come%20to%20Mizoram.%20Whether%20it%20is%20forced%20upon%20me%20or%20not%2C%20we%20have%20to%20act%20and%20find%20a%20solution%20for%20it%20as%20it%20affects%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%2012%2C000%20Kuki%20people%20displaced%20by%20the%20violence%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcant-manage-refugees-polls-alone-humanitarian-crisis-looms-mizoram-cms-sos-in-letter-to-modi%2F1688143%2F%3Famp%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esought%20refuge%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZoramthanga%20alleged%20that%20the%20union%20home%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20help%20to%20his%20administration%20in%20handling%20the%20influx%20of%20Kuki%20refugees%20into%20his%20state%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20enough%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20accepting%20Chin%20refugees%20fleeing%20the%20civil%20war%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20ethnically-related%20people%20leaving%20Bangladesh%20for%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20Bangladesh%20and%20Myanmar%20are%20concerned%20%E2%80%A6%20we%20are%20not%20signatory%20to%20UN%20Refugees.%20I%20told%20my%20chief%20secretary%20that%20we%20are%20merely%20following%20what%20%E2%80%A6%20India%20had%20done%20in%201970%20and%201971%20when%20millions%20of%20East%20Pakistan%20refugees%20had%20crossed%20over%20to%20India%20and%20%5Bwere%5D%20looked%20after%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20East%20Pakistan%20people%20were%20given%20that%20support%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20give%20it%20to%20people%20from%20Burma%2FMyanmar%3F%20The%20same%20formula%20has%20to%20be%20applied.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98No%20anger%20against%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EZoramthanga%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20while%20he%20was%20surprised%20by%20what%20he%20said%20were%20inadequate%20efforts%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20helping%20the%20refugees%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20violence%2C%20he%20would%20continue%20to%20remain%20a%20partner%20within%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20anger%20against%20the%20NDA%3B%20it%20has%20been%20constituted%20by%20a%20number%20of%20political%20parties%20to%20form%20an%20alliance.%20With%20the%20present%20Union%20government%2C%20I%20am%20a%20little%20surprised%20by%20their%20attitude%20in%20dealing%20with%20Manipur%20and%20not%20giving%20help%20to%20the%20refugees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20I%20requested%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%2C%20and%20the%20central%20government%20to%20look%20into%20the%20refugee%20and%20IDPs%E2%80%99%20crises%20from%20a%20different%20angle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20what%20it%20would%20take%20to%20end%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20violence%2C%20Zoramthanga%20said%20the%20following%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20solution%20is%2C%20let%20the%20Manipur%20and%20the%20central%20governments%20come%20together%20and%20consult%20the%20concerned%20people%20(Kuki%20and%20the%20Meitei%20people)%20and%20let%20the%20Union%20government%20settle%20this%20politically.%20That%20is%20the%20only%20solution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690623028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F20142741%2FZoramthanga.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fzoramthanga-on-ucc-and-manipur-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20to%20the%20Hindustan%20Times%2C%20Zoramthanga%20said%20his%20party%20would%20quit%20the%20NDA%20if%20a%20UCC%20was%20imposed%20on%20Mizoram.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fzoramthanga-on-ucc-and-manipur-violence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Star%20kids%20who%20did%20not%20choose%20an%20acting%20career%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690623000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102201634%2Cimgsize-45050.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faryan-khan-shaheen-bhatt-and-others-star-kids-who-did-not-follow-the-acting-path-like-their-parents%2Fphotostory%2F102201634.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102201634.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAryan%20Khan%2C%20Shaheen%20Bhatt%20and%20others%3A%20Star%20kids%20who%20did%20not%20follow%20the%20acting%20path%20like%20their%20parents%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tamannaah%20Danced%20To%20Kaavaalaa%20On%20Stage.%20Rajinikanth%20Was%20In%20The%20Audience%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamannaah-bhatia-refutes-reports-of-being-gifted-world-s-5th-largest-diamond-by-upasana-konidela-just-a-bottle-opener-4240778%5C%22%3ETamannaah%20Bhatia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20on%20a%20roll.%20Just%20a%20few%20days%20back%2C%20her%20d