format%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223538%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%20is%20based%20in%20Bracken%20House%20in%20the%20City%20of%20London.%3Cp%3EView%20Pictures%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20go%20and%20teach%20in%20an%20inner-city%20school%20in%20Hackney%20in%20east%20London%2C%20where%20about%2040%25%20were%20on%20free%20school%20meals%20and%20only%2015%25%20of%20students%20were%20white%2C%20was%20a%20shock%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20suddenly%20right%20up%20close%20to%20a%20world%20in%20which%20people%20were%20not%20like%20me.%20They%20didn't%20sound%20like%20me%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20weren't%20like%20me%20either.%20That%20is%20truly%20an%20interesting%20and%20exciting%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20first%20year%20as%20a%20teacher%20I%20was%20paid%20as%20a%20trainee%2C%20which%20was%20around%20%C2%A325%2C000%20(%2432%2C000).%20That%20was%20a%20significant%20salary%20cut%20from%20the%20more%20than%20%C2%A3100%2C000%20(%24128%2C000)%20I%20was%20earning%20as%20a%20columnist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20from%20public%20speaking%2C%20so%20my%20income%20took%20a%20huge%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20lucky%20because%20a%20year%20before%20I%20took%20the%20leap%20to%20become%20a%20teacher%20full-time%2C%20I%20stockpiled%20cash%20and%20have%20been%20cushioned%20by%20those%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20say%20that%20I'm%20living%20the%20life%20of%20a%20teacher%20who%20earns%20about%20%C2%A335%2C000%20(%2445%2C000)%20because%20I%20also%20have%20an%20FT%20pension.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20joined%20the%20school%20in%20Hackney%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20level%20of%C2%A0%20the%20dependence%20of%20families%20on%20food%20banks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20education%20'machine'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReal%20life%20is%20not%20like%20the%20Hollywood%20depiction%20of%20teaching.%20If%20you%20think%20of%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BDead%20Poets%20Society%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20the%20privileged%20white%20teacher%20has%20all%20the%20kids%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20the%20subject%20%E2%80%93%20it's%20not%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEducation%20is%20a%20system%20and%20a%20machine%20and%20actually%20the%20person%20who%20needs%20to%20do%20the%20adjusting%20isn't%20the%20kids%3B%20it's%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20a%20part%20of%20that%20system%20and%20the%20minute%20the%20machine%20says%20deliver%20the%20exam%20results%2C%20that's%20what%20you%20have%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20for%20me%20to%20leave%20readers%20with%20the%20impression%20that%20my%20life%20is%20like%20%26quot%3BDead%20Poets%20Society%26quot%3B%20couldn't%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20well%20as%20retraining%20to%20become%20a%20teacher%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20a%20charity%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnowteach.org.uk%2Fhow-to-become-a-teacher%2Fapply-for-teacher-training%2Fcan-i-train-part-time%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENow%20Teach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20supports%20people%20who%20want%20to%20retrain%20as%20teachers%20later%20in%20life%20to%20help%20fill%20the%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20from%20writing%20about%20working%20life%20that%20many%20people%20in%20their%20fifties%20who%20were%20lawyers%20or%20worked%20in%20other%20corporate%20roles%20get%20bored%20with%20it%20and%20want%20to%20do%20something%20more%20useful.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20about%20700%20people%20sign%20up%20to%20train%20as%20teachers.%20In%20the%20first%20year%20there%20were%20many%20corporate%20lawyers%2C%20ex-bankers%2C%20and%20consultants%20who%20joined.%20Now%20we're%20much%20broader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20do%20the%20training%20ourselves%20%E2%80%93%20we%20encourage%20and%20reassure%20the%20people%20signing%20up%20to%20become%20teachers.%20They%20come%20to%20the%20Now%20Teach%20website%2C%20we%20explain%20more%20about%20what%20it%20involves%20then%20we%20put%20them%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20training%20programs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFeeling%20great%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20this%20built-in%20network%20and%20support%20group%20of%20people%20who%20have%20done%20the%20same%20thing%2C%20and%20we%20offer%20a%20lot%20of%20networking%20and%20training%20sessions%20that%20are%20aimed%20specifically%20at%20this%20cohort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20employ%20about%2018%20to%2020%20people%20who%20work%20mainly%20part-time%20and%20they%20are%20involved%20in%20running%20the%20networks%20and%20then%20helping%20us%20select%20and%20recruit%20the%20candidates.%20I%20don't%20run%20it%20as%20I%20focus%20my%20time%20on%20teaching.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20journalist%2C%20I%20always%20felt%20that%20I'm%20only%20ever%20as%20good%20as%20my%20last%20piece.%20But%20as%20a%20teacher%2C%20after%20days%20where%20I%20feel%20I've%20taught%20a%20good%20lesson%2C%20I%20feel%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20on%20the%20days%20where%20I%20think%20I%20didn't%20teach%20very%20well%2C%20you%20can%20still%20say%20those%20students%20learned%20something%20new.%20All%20teachers%20have%20something%20positive%20to%20notch%20up%20every%20single%20day%20and%20that's%20amazing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucy%20Kellaway%20has%20written%20a%20number%20of%20books%2C%20most%20recently%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penguin.co.uk%2Fbooks%2F442314%2Fre-educated-by-kellaway-lucy%2F9781529108019%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERe-educated%3A%20Why%20it's%20never%20too%20late%20to%20change%20your%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20published%20by%20Penguin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-journalism-job-become-high-school-teacher-huge-culture-shock-202