ve%2C%20and%20that%20his%20efforts%20to%20keep%20his%20party%20united%20may%20also%20lead%20him%20to%20switch%20towards%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20such%20circumstances%2C%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20share%20the%20stage%20with%20Modi%20has%20had%20the%20rumour%20mills%20working%20overtime%2C%20and%20in%20the%20process%20creating%20greater%20confusion%20among%20opposition%20ranks.%20The%20event%20on%20August%201%20is%20being%20organised%20by%20the%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Smarak%20Mandir%20Trust%20to%20confer%20an%20award%20to%20Modi%20for%20his%20%E2%80%9Cleadership%20and%20efforts%20to%20instill%20a%20sense%20of%20patriotism%20among%20citizens%E2%80%9D.%20Pawar%20has%20been%20invited%20as%20the%20chief%20guest%20of%20the%20ceremony%20in%20which%20governor%20Ramesh%20Bais%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20BJP%20leader%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20are%20also%20among%20the%20VIP%20invitees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20two%20factions%20in%20the%20NCP%20spoke%20critically%20of%20each%20other%20in%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20the%20rebellion%2C%20both%20sides%20restrained%20themselves%20from%20attacking%20each%20other%20after%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20Praful%20Patel%20met%20the%20NCP%20supremo%20at%20his%20house%20recently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdisquiet-in-opposition-over-sharad-pawar-sharing-stage-with-modi-on-august-1%2Farticle67132012.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20INDIA%20parties%20on%20Friday%2C%20several%20opposition%20leaders%20flagged%20the%20issue%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20joining%20the%20event%20organised%20to%20award%20Modi.%20They%20believed%20that%20it%20would%20create%20bad%20%E2%80%9Coptics%E2%80%9D%20for