s.%20Pawar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fjul%2F29%2Fmaha-ruckus-in-house-over-pro-hindutva-leaders-jibe-at-mahatmas-parents-2599746.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20called%20a%20meeting%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20on%20Friday%20to%20discuss%20arrangements%20for%20the%20opposition%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20is%20said%20to%20have%20spoken%20to%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20too.%20Pawar%20has%20mooted%20the%20idea%20of%20organising%20a%20big%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20rally%20as%20a%20precursor%20to%20the%20opposition%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690619366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F11113000%2FSharad-Pawar.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdisquiet-in-opposition-ranks-as-sharad-pawar-set-to-share-stage-with-pm-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20event%20on%20August%201%20is%20being%20organised%20by%20the%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20Smarak%20Mandir%20Trust%20to%20confer%20an%20award%20to%20Modi%20for%20'leadership'.%20INDIA%20parties%20believe%20it%20will%20create%20bad%20'optics'%20for%20the%20opposition%20alliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdisquiet-in-opposition-ranks-as-sharad-pawar-set-to-share-stage-with-pm-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shooting%20in%20Seattle%20parking%20lot%20injures%205%20people%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690619324000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102229151%2Cimgsize-22570.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fshooting-in-seattle-parking-lot-injures-5-people-including-2-critically-police-chief-says%2Farticleshow%2F102229124.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102229124.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20shooting%20in%20a%20Seattle%20parking%20lot%20Friday%20night%20wounded%20five%20people%2C%20including%20two%20who%20were%20in%20critical%20condition%2C%20the%20city's%20police%20chief%20said.%20The%20Seattle%20Police%20Department%20responded%20to%20a%20reported%20shooting%20around%209%20p.m.%20in%20the%209200%20block%20of%20Rainier%20Avenue%20South.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fshooting-in-seattle-parking-lot-injures-5-people-including-2-critically-police-chief-says%2Farticleshow%2F102229124.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fshooting-in-seattle-parking-lot-injures-5-people-including-2-critically-police-chief-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F102229124.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fshooting-in-seattle-parking-lot-injures-5-people-including-2-critically-police-chief-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F102229124.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Makes%20Ex%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20Vice%20Chancellor%20Party%20Vice%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20strengthen%20its%20ongoing%20outreach%20among%20Muslim%20Pasmanda%20communities%2C%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-bjp-rejigs-team-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-head-tariq-mansoor-gets-top-post-4250612%5C%22%3Eon%20Saturday%20appointed%3C%2Fa%3E%20former%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20vice-chancellor%20Tariq%20Mansoor%20as%20one%20of%20its%20vice%20presidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mansoor%20was%20instrumental%20in%20steering%20the%20AMU%2C%20one%20of%20the%20hotbeds%20of%20anti-NRC%20and%20CAA%20protests%2C%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bmiddle%20path%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20later%20closely%20working%20with%20the%20RSS%20on%20its%20project%20to%20promote%20the%20teachings%20of%20Mughal%20prince%20Dara%20Shikoh%20on%20peaceful%20Hindu-Muslim%20coexistence%20that%20was%20in%20contradiction%20to%20his%20brother%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb's%20way%20of%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20was%20in%20Rameshwaram%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20launch%20a%20book%20on%20former%20president%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20also%20one%20of%20the%20icons%20of%20the%20party's%20Pasmanda%20outreach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20has%20been%20continuously%20reaching%20out%20to%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Muslim%20population%20through%20Minority%20Morcha%20meetings%2C%20mostly%20focused%20on%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%2C%20who%20are%20from%20Dalit%20and%20other%20backward%20class%20communities.%20Mr%20Mansoor%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Legislative%20Council%2C%20the%20fourth%20Muslim%20picked%20by%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20post%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETariq%20Mansoor%20is%20from%20Aligarh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20Muslims%20constitute%20roughly%2019%25%20of%20the%20state's%20electorate%2C%20and%20have%20a%20sizeable%20presence%20in%20at%20least%2030%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20out%20of%20which%20they%20play%20a%20major%20role%20in%20deciding%20the%20outcome%20in%2015%20to%2020%20constituencies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20RSS%20functionary%2C%20Mr%20Mansoor%20had%20impressed%20the%20sangh's%20leadership%20by%20his%20work%20on%20the%20Dara%20Shikoh%20project%2C%20by%20effectively%20using%20the%20AMU's%20Persian%20department%20to%20translate%20much%20of%20Shikoh's%20work%20on%20inter-faith%20dialogue%20and%20project%20him%20as%20an%20ideal%20for%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20He%20organised%20seminars%20and%20conferences%20on%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mansoor%2C%20a%20surgeon%2C%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20AMU%20since%20the%201970s%20when%20he%20completed%20his%20MBBS%20degree%20in%20surgery%20from%20the%20university's%20JN%20Medical%20College.%20He%20then%20went%20on%20to%20do%20his%20Master%20of%20Surgery%20(MS)%20degree%20in%201982%20from%20the%20same%20college.%20Apart%20from%20the%20BJP's%20focus%20on%20the%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%2C%20which%20is%20important%20in%20terms%20of%20influence%2C%20the%20RSS%20has%20been%20specifically%20reaching%20out%20to%20Muslim%20academics%2C%20and%20people%20of%20the%20community%20from%20professions%20such%20as%20medicine%2C%20law%2C%20and%20bureaucracy%2C%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20the%20minority%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20Siddiqui%2C%20head%20of%20the%20BJP's%20Minority%20Morcha%20said%20Mr%20Mansoor%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bnationalist%20Muslim%26quot%3B%20who%20has%20always%20promoted%20the%20ideal%20of%20%26quot%3Bnation%20first.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHis%20understanding%20of%20the%20fault%20lines%20in%20the%20Muslim%20community%20is%20as%20deep%20as%20his%20knowledge%20about%20the%20country%20and%20its%20history.%20He%20has%20led%20the%20students%20of%20AMU%20on%20the%20right%20path%20and%20prevented%20them%20from%20being%20misled.%20His%20appointment%20will%20help%20the%20party%20to%20expand%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20fourth%20person%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20to%20be%20promoted%20to%20the%20Legislative%20Council%20by%20the%20party%20in%20UP%20since%202017%2C%20after%20Bukkal%20Nawab%2C%20Mohsin%20Raza%2C%20and%20Danish%20Azad%20Ansari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mansoor%20was%20the%20AMU%20Vice%20Chancellor%20when%20it%20witnessed%20protests%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20the%20proposed%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20in%202020.%20He%20was%20then%20criticised%20for%20%26quot%3Bnot%20standing%20up%20for%20students%26quot%3B%20when%20policemen%20allegedly%20barged%20into%20the%20university%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20VC%20of%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%20in%20Delhi%2C%20who%20stood%20by%20the%20students.%20Mr%20Mansoor%20has%2C%20however%2C%20always%20said%20he%20did%20his%20best%2C%20and%20talked%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20welfare%20and%20socio-economic%20justice%20over%20identity%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMansoor%20belongs%20to%20Aligarh%2C%20the%20hub%20of%20Muslim%20politics%2C%20and%20comes%20from%20an%20educated%2C%20middle%20class%20family.%20His%20family%20has%20doctors%20and%20lawyers.%20This%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20Muslims%20we%20want%20to%20work%20with%20to%20take%20the%20nation%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BJP%20functionary%20from%20UP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalid%20Anis%20Ansari%2C%20associate%20professor%20from%20Azim%20Premji%20University%2C%20who%20has%20been%20actively%20raising%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20the%20community%20for%20many%20years%2C%20has%20often%20pointed%20out%20that%20Indian%20Muslims%20too%20are%20victims%20of%20caste-based%20stratification%2C%20and%20are%20divided%20into%20three%20main%20classes%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20biradaris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Ashraf'%20Muslims%2C%20or%20native%20upper%20caste%20converts%2C%20for%20instance%20Syed%2C%20Sheikh%2C%20Mughal%2C%20Pathan%2C%20etc%20are%20at%20the%20top%2C%20and%20the%20Syed%20biradari%20is%20highly%20revered.%20The%20movements%20against%20the%20Ashraf%20dominance%20have%20been%20led%20by%20the%20'lower'%20ones%20-%20Ajlaf%20(backward%20Muslims)%20and%20Arzal%20(Dalit%20Muslims)%2C%20and%20these%20are%20known%20as%20Pasmandas%2C%20the%20community%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20woo.%20Only%2015%20percent%20of%20the%20community%20come%20from%20these%20upper%20caste%20communities%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20are%20largely%20Pasmanda%20Muslims.%20The%20BJP%20has%20planned%20a%20massive%20Sneh%20Yatra%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20these%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20intellectuals%20and%20opposition%20parties%20have%2C%20however%2C%20said%20this%20was%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20create%20a%20divide%20among%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20and%20that%20often%20the%20Muslim%20victims%20of%20hate%20crimes%20or%20economic%20boycott%20were%20Pasmanda%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690618920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F36lv01r_tariq-mansoor_625x300_04_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftariq-mansoor-appointed-bjp-vice-president-pasmanda-muslims-jp-nadda-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-vc-who-promoted-dara-shikohs-syncretism-made-bjp-vic-4250713%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20attempt%20to%20strengthen%20its%20ongoing%20outreach%20among%20Muslim%20Pasmanda%20communities%2C%20the%20BJP%20on%20Sunday%20appointed%20former%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20vice-chancellor%20Tariq%20Mansoor%20as%20one%20of%20its%20vice%20presidents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftariq-mansoor-appointed-bjp-vice-president-pasmanda-muslims-jp-nadda-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-vc-who-promoted-dara-shikohs-syncretism-made-bjp-vic-4250713%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftariq-mansoor-appointed-bjp-vice-president-pasmanda-muslims-jp-nadda-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-vc-who-promoted-dara-shikohs-syncretism-made-bjp-vic-4250713%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftariq-mansoor-appointed-bjp-vice-president-pasmanda-muslims-jp-nadda-ex-aligarh-muslim-university-vc-who-promoted-dara-shikohs-syncretism-made-bjp-vic-4250713%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sanjay%20Drops%20First%20Look%20As%20Big%20Bull%20From%20Puri%20Jagannadh's%20Double%20ISMART%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20occasion%20of%20his%2064th%20birthday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsa