%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Feight-die-in-krishnagiri-firecracker-godown-accident%2Farticleshow%2F102228687.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eye%20On%202024%20Polls%2C%20BJP%20Makes%20Major%20Changes%20To%20Central%20Team.%20Details%20Here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBJP%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20rejigged%20the%20list%20of%20the%20party's%20central%20office-bearers%20today%2C%20bringing%20in%20a%20Pasmanda%20Muslim%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20one%20of%20its%20Vice%20Presidents%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Telangana%20unit%20chief%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20was%20appointed%20national%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20dropped%20CT%20Ravi%2C%20a%20leader%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20Dilip%20Saikia%2C%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Assam%2C%20as%20its%20general%20secretaries%2C%20and%20Vinod%20Sonkar%2C%20Harish%20Dwivedi%2C%20both%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Sunil%20Deodhar%20as%20secretaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadha%20Mohan%20Agrawal%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20two%20new%20faces%20on%20the%20list%20which%20have%20nine%20general%20secretaries%2C%20seven%20of%20whom%20retain%20their%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20secretaries%20are%20Anil%20Antony%2C%20son%20of%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%20AK%20Antony%2C%20and%20Surendra%20Singh%20Nagar%20and%20Kamakhya%20Prasad%20Tasa%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20UP%20and%20Assam%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nagar%20is%20an%20influential%20Gurjar%20leader%20from%20western%20UP%20while%20Mr%20Tasa%20has%20long%20been%20the%20face%20of%20tea%20tribes%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2013%20vice%20presidents%2C%20nine%20general%20secretaries%2C%20including%20BL%20Santhosh%20as%20the%20in-charge%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20and%2013%20secretaries%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Union%20minister%20Radha%20Mohan%20Singh%2C%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Bihar%2C%20has%20been%20dropped%20from%20the%20post%20of%20party%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20BJP%20president%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Laxmikant%20Bajpai%20is%20one%20of%20the%20two%20new%20vice%20presidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Tariq%20Mansoor%20being%20inducted%20as%20a%20party%20vice%20president%2C%20there%20are%20two%20Muslims%20in%20the%20position%20now.%20Kerala%20leader%20Abdulla%20Kutty%20is%20another%20member%20from%20the%20minority%20community%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20former%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20(AMU)%20Vice-Chancellor%20Tariq%20Mansoor%2C%20now%20a%20BJP%20MLC%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20party's%20overtures%20to%20Pasmanda%20(backward)%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ravi's%20omission%20from%20the%20list%20of%20general%20secretaries%2C%20who%20spearhead%20the%20party's%20policies%20and%20agenda%20nationally%20and%20state-wise%2C%20unlike%20the%20vice%20presidents%20who%20are%20mostly%20figureheads%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20by%20some%20as%20a%20fallout%20of%20the%20BJP's%20big%20defeat%20in%20the%20recent%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-term%20MLA%20had%20lost%20his%20seat%20in%20a%20close%20fight%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20party%20leader%20said%20not%20much%20should%20be%20read%20into%20the%20dropping%20of%20several%20office-bearers%2C%20as%20many%20of%20them%2C%20including%20Ravi%2C%20may%20contest%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20will%20be%20focussing%20on%20their%20likely%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20weeks%20after%20his%20removal%20as%20the%20Telangana%2