agement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fnortheast-diary-disguised-as-refugees-kuki-chin-militants-from-bangladesh-entered-mizoram%2Farticleshow%2F102228283.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Firms%20Can%20Now%20List%20On%20Gujarat%20Finance%20Hub%20To%20Draw%20Foreign%20Funds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20has%20allowed%20its%20firms%20to%20list%20on%20exchanges%20registered%20in%20a%20new%20financial%20hub%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20on%20Friday%2C%20to%20give%20companies%20access%20to%20easier%20and%20cheaper%20foreign%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListed%20and%20unlisted%20companies%20can%20list%20their%20shares%20in%20the%20International%20Financial%20Services%20Centre%20(IFSC)%20housed%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20International%20Financial%20Tech%20City%20(GIFT)%2C%20which%20is%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20flagship%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20pleased%20to%20announce%20that%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20decision%20to%20enable%20direct%20listing%20of%20listed%20and%20unlisted%20companies%20on%20the%20IFSC%20exchanges%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGIFT-IFSC%20is%20a%20tax%20neutral%20financial%20center%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20compete%20with%20hubs%20like%20Singapore%20as%20it%20provides%20fiscal%20incentives%20and%20an%20easier%20regulatory%20environment%20to%20operate%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20SGX%20Nifty%2C%20which%20was%20previously%20traded%20on%20the%20Singapore%20Exchange's%20(SGX)%20platform%2C%20moved%20to%20NSE's%20International%20Exchange%20(NSE%20IX)%20in%20GIFT%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IFSC%20houses%20two%20stock%20exchanges%2C%20one%20commodity%20bourse%2C%20and%20a%20bullion%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20companies%20can%20currently%20only%20list%20on%20foreign%20exchanges%20through