aghat%20which%20the%20latter%20had%20called%20an%20instance%20of%20%E2%80%9Clove-jihad%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Borah%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fassam-cong-chief-apologises-for-bringing-up-lord-krishna-in-response-to-cms-love-jihad-claim-8865751%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20cross-marrying%20%E2%80%9Cis%20not%20a%20new%20thing%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20are%20many%20examples%20in%20history%E2%80%9D%20when%20he%20gave%20lord%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20with%20Rukmini%20as%20an%20example%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20July%2027%2C%20Sarma%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20leader%20would%20be%20arrested%20if%20an%20FIR%20is%20filed%20against%20him%20for%20making%20contentious%20statements%20regarding%20lord%20Krishna%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Silchar%20unit%20of%20BJYM%20and%20BJP%20workers%20in%20Bajali%20also%20filed%20FIRs%20against%20Borah%20in%20their%20respective%20districts%20and%20demanded%20immediate%20action%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20July%2028%2C%20Borah%20apologised%20for%20his%20comment%20on%20lord%20Krishna%20claiming%20that%20his%20grandfather%20appeared%20to%20him%20in%20a%20dream%20and%20told%20him%20his%20words%20were%20wrong%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fassam-cong-chief-apologises-for-bringing-up-lord-krishna-in-response-to-cms-love-jihad-claim-8865751%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fassam-cong-chief-apologises-for-bringing-up-lord-krishna-in-response-to-cms-love-jihad-claim-8865751%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20apologising%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20but%20because%20his%20comments%20might%20not%20have%20been%20well%20received%20by%20the%20Vaishnavite%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20requested%20for%20my%20arrest.%20I%20was%20instructed%20to%20stop%20visiting%20Namghars.%20I%20beg%20them%20not%20to%20prevent%20me%20from%20going%20to%20Namghars.%20Instead%2C%20shoot%20me%20dead%20during%20a%20police%20encounter%2C%E2%80%9D%20Borah%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EAssam%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorah%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20police%20had%20not%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20him%20yet%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20genuine%20slip%20of%20tongue%E2%80%9D%20for%20which%20he%20apologised%20profusely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20country%2C%20if%20you%20are%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebhakt%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethen%20%3Cem%3Esau%20khoon%20maaf%3C%2Fem%3E%20(you%20are%20allowed%20a%20hundred%20crimes).%20But%20if%20you%20are%20not%2C%20one%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20all%20kinds%20of%20harassment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Borah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20questioned%20why%20those%20who%20threaten%20genocide%20are%20not%20pursued%20with%20the%20same%20proactiveness%2C%20alluding%20to%20Pramot%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20%E2%80%93%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-meitei-leepun-pramot-singh-karan-thapar-manipur-violence-kukis%5C%22%3Eopenly%20expressed%20his%20contempt%20for%20the%20Kuki%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20term%20often%20brought%20up%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20affiliates%2C%20claiming%20that%20Muslim%20men%20are%20luring%20and%20forcing%20Hindu%20women%20into%20marriage%20to%20convert%20them.%20No%20empirical%20evidence%20has%20been%20found%20for%20such%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690614637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3