3EM.M.%20War%E2%80%99s%20letter%20to%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20M.M.%20War%E2%80%99s%20letterhead%2C%20he%20is%20a%20member%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20state%20executive%20committee%20and%20national%20executive%20member%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Kissan%20Morcha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claims%20that%20he%20is%20also%20in-charge%20of%20the%20party%20in%20north%20Kashmir%20and%20Prabhari%20of%20Baramulla%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20M.M.%20War%20has%20claimed%20that%20these%20police%20officers%20were%20targeting%20BJP%20leaders%20for%20the%20past%20one%20month%20and%20were%20not%20investigating%20leaders%20of%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20other%20big%20fishes%2C%20who%2C%20he%20said%2C%20should%20have%20been%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20further%20writes%20that%20they%20are%20working%20round-the-clock%20for%20the%20benefit%20and%20betterment%20of%20the%20party%2C%20but%20these%20officials%20were%20not%20cooperating%20with%20the%20party%20leaders%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respond%20to%20their%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20their%20transfer%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20has%20demanded%20that%20only%20officers%20who%20will%20cooperate%20with%20the%20party%20leaders%20should%20be%20posted%20in%20lieu%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20even%20proposed%20the%20names%20of%20two%20police%20officers%20as%20their%20replacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Amod%20Ashok%20Nagpure%2C%20an%20IPS%20officer%20of%20the%202013%20batch%2C%20is%20SSP%20Baramulla%2C%20Shabir%20Nawab%2C%20an%20officer%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Police%20Service%20(JKPS)%20of%20the%202001%20batch%2C%20is%20SSP%20Sopore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leader%20has%20sought%20the%20transfer%20of%20these%20officers%20days%20after%20police%20arrested%20Ashiq%20Ganie%20aka%20Ashiq%20MLA%2C%20who%20is%20affiliated%20with%20BJP%2C%20on%20charges%20of%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20Ashiq%20MLA%20and%20two%20others%20affiliated%20with%20a%20political%20party%20approached%20a%20person%20to%20get%20his%20brother%20released%20from%20custody%20and%20demanded%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20person%20sold%20his%20land%20and%20provided%20them%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20get%20his%20brother%20released%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20accused%20persons%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20the%20detenue%20released%20from%20custody%20thus%20the%20complainant%20demanded%20his%20money%20back%20from%20the%20accused%20persons.%20But%20the%20accused%20persons%20demanded%20more%20money%20from%20the%20complainant%20and%20warned%20that%20if%20they%20did%20not%20pay%20the%20amount%20they%20will%20face%20serious%20repercussions%20and%20will%20get%20his%20brother%20booked%20in%20multiple%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20a%20handout%20issued%20by%20Baramulla%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshiq%20MLA%20is%20the%20municipal%20councillor%20of%20Baramulla%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20police%20arrested%20another%20BJP%20leader%20Mudasir%20Ahmad%20Wani%20on%20extortion%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWani%20and%20his%20accomplice%20Yasir%20Rashid%20Rather%20had%20demanded%20Rs%201%20lakh%20from%20a%20family%20to%20get%20a%20PSA%20detainee%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PSA%20detainee%20was%20released%20by%20police%20after%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20quashed%20his%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20threatened%20his%20family%20that%20they%20will%20get%20him%20re-detained%20if%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20cough%20up%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20damage-control%20move%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20distanced%20itself%20from%20its%20leader%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20saying%20the%20party%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20views%20expressed%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20media%20through%20his