r%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.earthreminder.com%2Fhow-does-carpooling-help-the-environment%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGreenhouse%2520gas%2520emissions%2520can%2520be%2Cis%2520released%2520into%2520the%2520environment.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduces%20emissions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Delhi%20government%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.autocarindia.com%2Findustry%2Fdelhi-government-to-offer-incentives-with-new-ev-policy-415370%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20subsidies%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20facilitate%20buying%20of%20e-rickshaws%20and%20installed%20public%20charging%20stations%20across%20the%20city.%20Now%2C%20drivers%20can%20exchange%20their%20discharged%20batteries%20for%20fully%20charged%20ones%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Findia-electric-rickshaw-revolution-low-carbon-future-1.6642423%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattery-swapping%20shops%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Delhi%20races%20to%20become%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frestofworld.org%2F2022%2Findia-electric-vehicle-capital%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEV%20capital%20of%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20photo%20essay%20documents%20the%20hopes%2C%20aspirations%2C%20fears%2C%20and%20challenges%20of%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%93NCR.%20It%20attempts%20to%20highlight%20the%20drivers%20pivoting%20the%20cities%E2%80%99%20sustainable%20transport%20revolution%2C%20understand%20what%20this%20transition%20means%20for%20them%20and%20their%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20underline%20the%20issues%20that%20still%20trouble%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20better%20life%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20spoke%20with%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20in%20Ghaziabad%20and%20Delhi%20and%20found%20that%20many%20of%20them%20are%20migrants%20from%20rural%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjinesh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20driving%20an%20e-rickshaw%20around%20the%20Indirapuram%20residential%20area%20in%20Ghaziabad%20for%20two%20years%20now%2C%20moved%20to%20Ghaziabad%20from%20Hamirpur%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20search%20of%20a%20better%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20drive%20a%20rented%20autorickshaw%20in%20the%20village.%20I%20would%20earn%20INR%201%2C700%E2%80%931%2C900%20a%20day%2C%20and%20from%20that%2C%20I%20would%20pay%20the%20owner%20INR%20500%20daily%20and%20fill%20INR%20200%20worth%20of%20gas%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcng.co.tt%2Fwhat-is-cng%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNG%3C%2Fa%3E).%20My%20uncle%20who%20lives%20in%20this%20city%20asked%20me%20to%20come%20here%20and%20try%20my%20luck.%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20drive%20an%20auto%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20competition%20among%20autos.%20There%20were%20fewer%20e-rickshaws%20at%20that%20time%2C%20so%20I%20rented%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164353%2FAjinesh-explains-the-nuances-of-driving-an-e-rickshaw-in-Ghaziabad.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164353%2FAjinesh-explains-the-nuances-of-driving-an-e-rickshaw-in-Ghaziabad.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164353%2FAjinesh-explains-the-nuances-of-driving-an-e-rickshaw-in-Ghaziabad-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665652%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAjinesh%20explains%20what%20is%20it%20to%20drive%20an%20e-rickshaw%20in%20Ghaziabad.%20Photo%3A%20Debojit%20Dutta%20and%20Srishti%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjinesh%20pays%20INR%20300%20as%20rent%20for%20the%20e-rickshaw%20and%20spends%20INR%20210%20on%20the%20rechargeable%20batteries%2C%20which%20he%20swaps%20three%20times%20a%20day%20at%20battery%20swapping%20centres%20across%20the%20city.%20He%20drives%20his%20e-rickshaw%20from%20Ghaziabad%20to%20Noida%20and%20ferries%20passengers%20and%20goods%20too.%20Initially%2C%20this%20was%20profitable%20and%20he%20used%20to%20make%20INR%201%2C500%20a%20day%2C%20but%20as%20more%20people%20started%20driving%20e-rickshaws%2C%20his%20income%20started%20to%20reduce.%20Now%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20workday%2C%20Ajinesh%20is%20left%20with%20the%20same%20INR%20800%E2%80%931%2C000%20that%20he%20used%20to%20make%20driving%20the%20auto%20in%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20e-rickshaws%20posed%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20auto%20drivers%20when%20they%20started%20taking%20over%20the%20road.%20Now%2C%20the%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20are%20competing%20among%20themselves%20as%20their%20numbers%20have%20increased%20significantly%2C%20especially%20in%20residential%20areas%20and%20for%20commuting%20to%20and%20from%20the%20metro.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20starts%20driving%20at%208%20am%20and%20finishes%20work%20at%2010%20pm.%20This%2014-hour%20shift%20is%20a%20marked%20increase%20from%20the%20eight%20or%20nine%20hours%20he%20used%20to%20spend%20driving%20his%20auto.%20Ajinesh%20admits%20that%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20enough%20time%20to%20spend%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20their%2011-month-old%20child.%20He%20is%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20only%20earning%20member.%20As%20expenses%20at%20home%20are%20bound%20to%20increase%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20buy%20his%20own%20e-rickshaw%20and%20save%20the%20money%20he%20pays%20in%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20buy%20a%20metal%20rickshaw%2C%20which%20is%20sturdier%20than%20the%20plastic%20variant%20I%20am%20driving%20now.%20They%20are%20available%20for%20INR%201%2C75%2C000%20on%20EMI%20at%20the%20showrooms%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE-rickshaw%20drivers%20like%20Ajinesh%20say%20that%20the%20interest%20on%20the%20loan%20is%20anywhere%20between%2017%25%20and%2020%25%2C%20which%20is%20a%20substantial%20amount.%20There%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20down%20payment%20of%20INR%2040%E2%80%9350%2C000.%20As%20many%20people%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20pay%20these%20amounts%2C%20they%20rent%20a%20vehicle.%20The%20Delhi%20government%20is%20providing%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fev.delhi.gov.in%2Fbrands-dealers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurchase%20incentive%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20INR%2030%2C000%20on%20buying%20e-rickshaws%20and%20a%205%25%20interest%20subsidy%20on%20loans%2C%20but%20this%20is%20limited%20to%20certain%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDilip%20Ram%2C%20an%20e-rickshaw%20driver%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Govindpuri%20area%20who%20migrated%20from%20Bihar%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20brands%20in%20the%20market%20now%20and%20the%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20trust%20the%20new%20players.%20There%E2%80%99s%20subsidy%20but%20people%20who%20applied%20for%20it%20have%20been%20waiting%20to%20receive%20those%20for%20two%E2%80%93three%20years%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avail%20the%20government%20subsidies%2C%20the%20drivers%20must%20have%20documents%20such%20as%20Aadhaar%20card%20and%20electricity%20bills%20for%20residential%20proof%2C%20with%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%20from%20the%20landlord%20in%20case%20of%20rented%20housing.%20Documentation%20is%20often%20a%20challenge%20for%20migrant%20workers.%20Dilip%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20easier%20to%20get%20second-hand%20lead-acid-battery-operated%20rickshaws%20for%20INR%2030%E2%80%9340%2C000.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20lead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20lithium-ion-battery-run%20vehicle%20that%20Dilip%20drives%20is%20a%20more%20recent%20phenomenon%2C%20e-rickshaws%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fblog%2Fair%2Fwhy-e-rickshaws-have-emerged-a-winner-in-transition-to-electric-mobility-race-75767%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowered%20by%20lead%20batteries%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0have%20been%20plying%20the%20Delhi%E2%80%93NCR%20roads%20since%202012%20when%20they%20were%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fsheila-dikshit-asks-transport-department-to-frame-e-rickshaw-policy%2Farticleshow%2F17377492.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunched%20with%20much%20fanfare%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.who.int%2Firis%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F10665%2F259447%2F9789241512855-eng.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoon%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0started%20being%20raised%20about%20the%20environmental%20and%20health%20impact%20of%20recycling%20lead%20batteries.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20replaced%20as%20they%20run%20out%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.abplive.com%2Fauto%2Fe-rickshaw-battery-management-india-price-fame-state-plan-delhi-assam-schemes-policies-management-of-three-wheels-of-electric-vehicles-revolution-1614798%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevery%20six%20to%20eight%20months%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2022%2F12%2F12%2Fexactly-how-environment-friendly-are-delhis-e-rickshaws%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20detailed%2C%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20sell%20these%20batteries%20to%20dealers%20and%20buy%2