ce%20for%20lithium-run%20rickshaws%20will%20continue%20to%20buy%20lead-battery-operated%20e-rickshaws%20even%20if%20they%20have%20to%20pay%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fghaziabad%2Fe-rickshaws-everywhere-but-most-illegal-in-ghaziabad-drivers-dont-have-permits-either%2Farticleshow%2F97469168.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoccasional%20fine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECarrying%20the%20load%20alone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDilip%20says%20that%20if%20the%20drivers%20received%20some%20help%20with%20documentation%2C%20more%20people%20could%20adapt%20to%20the%20change.%20To%20understand%20why%20they%20need%20support%2C%20one%20can%20consider%20the%20example%20of%20Chandan%2C*%20an%20e-rickshaw%20driver%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Govindpuri%20locality.%20He%20could%20not%20avail%20the%20subsidies%20because%20his%20disability%20limits%20his%20movement.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20knowing%20about%20the%20subsidy%2C%20I%20could%20not%20go%20and%20apply%20for%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20auto%20drivers%2C%20e-rickshaws%20have%20no%20unions%20that%20often%20help%20with%20awareness.%20Bharat%2C%20who%20shifted%20from%20riding%20an%20auto%20to%20buying%20his%20own%20e-rickshaw%20during%20the%20lockdown%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnless%20we%20have%20a%20union%2C%20no%20one%20will%20listen%20to%20us.%20You%20need%20a%20union%20to%20take%20an%20issue%20to%20the%20authorities%20and%20even%20to%20have%20a%20conversation%20within%20your%20own%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164657%2FBharat-in-his-e-rickshaw-explaining-the-need-for-a-union.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5