ing%20ahead%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20issues%2C%20Dilip%20says%20e-rickshaws%20make%20more%20sense%20because%20purchasing%20an%20autorickshaw%20costs%20INR%207%E2%80%938%20lakh.%20Drivers%20such%20as%20Dilip%20and%20Bharat%20have%20installed%20EV%20charging%20facilities%20at%20their%20homes.%20It%20costs%20them%20INR%2060%20per%20day%20for%20a%20full%20charge%2C%20which%20takes%20up%20to%20six%E2%80%93eight%20hours%20and%20lets%20the%20vehicle%20run%20for%20100%20km.%20It%20helps%20that%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mongabay.com%2F2022%2F07%2Felectric-vehicle-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEV%20charging%20tariff%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20homes%20is%20among%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20means%20to%20charge%20at%20home%20can%20use%20the%20multiple%20public%20charging%20stations%20that%20the%20state%20has%20installed.%20However%2C%20here%20they%20have%20to%20pay%20INR%20100%20for%20a%20full%20charge.%20Most%20of%20the%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20park%20their%20vehicles%20at%20the%20municipality%20parking%20areas%20at%20night%20and%20take%20them%20out%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20cost%20of%20charging%20at%20the%20station%20can%20still%20be%20quite%20high%20for%20many%20people.%20Those%20like%20Ajinesh%2C%20who%20often%20travel%20more%20than%20100%20km%2C%20prefer%20swapping%20their%20batteries%20instead.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20have%20been%20times%20when%20I%20have%20run%20out%20of%20batteries%20on%20the%20road.%20I%20would%20immediately%20take%20my%20rickshaw%20to%20a%20battery-swapping%20station%20nearby.%20They%20charge%20INR%20150%20for%20the%20first%20battery%20and%20INR%2070%20after%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20for%20EVs%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fauto%2Fdelhi-to-get-more-ev-charging-battery-swapping-stations-ndmc-vice-chairman-satish-upadhyay-7791913.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiven%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20both%20private-%20and%20gove%20rnment-owned%20swapping%20stations.%20However%2C%20there%20have%20been%20safety%20concerns%20regarding%20these%20since%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyourstory.com%2F2023%2F04%2Fbattery-smart-swapping-station-fire-delhi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enews%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20multiple%20such%20places%20catching%20fire%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovernance%2Fwhy-e-rickshaws-are-no-big-draw-for-delhi-drivers-despite-kejriwal-govts-purchase-subsidy%2F915787%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0published%20a%20report%20where%20many%20people%20emphasised%20cost%2C%20fear%20of%20the%20vehicles%20being%20stolen%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20awareness%20about%20government%20initiatives%20as%20reasons%20for%20not%20embracing%20the%20e-rickshaw%20wave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%2C*%20who%20drives%20a%20CNG%20auto%20in%20South%20Delhi%20and%20also%20has%20an%20electric%20auto%20that%20his%20father%20drives%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20difference%20in%20income%20between%20the%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20and%20auto%20drivers%20for%20me%20to%20want%20to%20make%20the%20shift.%20CNG%20stations%20are%20more%20easily%20available%20than%20EV%20charging%20stations%2C%20which%20are%20mostly%20concentrated%20in%20South%20Delhi.%20I%20might%20be%20paying%20INR%20250%20to%20fill%20the%20tank%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20hours%20to%20charge%20my%20vehicle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CE-rickshaws%20should%20run%20for%20at%20least%20200%20km%20on%20a%20single%20charge%20and%20have%20fast%20charging.%20It%20works%20for%20my%20father%20because%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20go%20very%20far%2C%20but%20he%20struggles%20with%20connecting%20the%20charger%20every%20night.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%3Cem%3ENames%20changed%20to%20maintain%20confidentiality%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20in%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fidronline.org%2F%5C%22%3EIndian%20Development%20Review%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Cem%3ERead%20the%20original%20piece%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fidronline.org%2Farticle%2Flivelihoods%2Fphoto-essay-e-rickshaw-drivers-ferry-indias-electric-dream%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690597855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28164221%2FFeature-image_An-e-rickshaw-accompanies-daily-life-in-South-Delhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fdocumentation-bad-roads-and-charging-costs-challenges-galore-for-delhi-e-rickshaw-drivers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20of%20the%20e-rickshaw%20drivers%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20are%20migrants%20from%20rural%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20who%20either%20lack%20awareness%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20unions%20or%20do%20not%20make%20the%20cut%20to%20avail%20Delhi%20government's%20subsidies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fdocumentation-bad-roads-and-charging-costs-challenges-galore-for-delhi-e-rickshaw-drivers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%3A%20Partially%20Disabled%20Bone%20Factory%20Worker%20Lynched%20on%20Suspicion%20of%20Cattle%20Theft%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201937%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.30-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhopal%20(MP)%2FChapra%20(Bihar)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20man%20in%20Bihar%20was%20lynched%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20at%20least%2070%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20smuggling%20beef.%20Fifty-five-year-old%20Zahiruddin%20was%20a%20truck%20driver%20who%20worked%20for%20an%20animal%20bones%20supplier%20and%20byproduct%20manufacturer.%20He%20had%20been%20transporting%20animal%20bones%20%E2%80%93%20an%20essential%20component%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20when%20he%20was%20killed.%20Because%20he%20was%20partially%20disabled%20on%20one%20of%20his%20legs%2C%20he%20could%20not%20run%20from%20the%20mob%2C%20say%20his%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20June%2028%2C%20a%20day%20before%20Bakrid%2C%20in%20the%20Paigambarpur%20village%20of%20Saran%20district%20in%20Bihar.%20Saran%20is%20also%20known%20as%20Chhapra%2C%20after%20the%20district%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZahiruddin%20worked%20for%20what%20is%20commonly%20called%20a%20%E2%80%98bone%20mill%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20factory%20that%20takes%20cattle%20bones%20and%20manufactures%20a%20powder%20that%20is%20essential%20to%20the%20production%20of%20gelatin%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20is%20used%20widely%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%2C%20cosmetic%20and%20health%20supplements%20industry%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2029%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Jalalpura%20Police%20Station%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20six%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20Prakash%20Singh%2C%20Sunil%20Singh%2C%20Kallu%2C%20Tribhuvan%20Singh%2C%20Anup%20Singh%2C%20Pramod%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20and%2030%20unnamed%20others%20under%20Sections%20342%20(punishment%20for%20wrongful%20confinement)%2C%20147%20(punishment%20for%20rioting)%2C%20148%20(rioting%2C%20armed%20with%20a%20deadly%20weapon)%2C%20149%20(unlawful%20assembly)%20and%20302%20(murder)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20named%20accused%2C%20Sunil%20Singh%2C%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Emukhiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20chief%20of%20Paigambarpur%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20the%20Station%20House%20Officer%20of%20Jalalpura%20Police%20Station%2C%20Pintu%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20have%20successfully%20identified%20and%20apprehended%20seven%20previously%20unknown%20suspects%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20innocent%20individuals%20involved.%20The%20police%20have%20obtained%20CCTV%20footage%20as%20part%20of%20the%20investigation.%20We%20are%20awaiting%20supervision%20and%20guidance%20from%20senior%20officers.%20Any%20further%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20orders%20given%20by%20the%20higher%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20informed%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fact-finding%20team%20of%20the%20Association%20for%20Protection%20of%20Civil%20Rights%20visited%20Zahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Marhaura.%20One%20of%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20report%2C%20Saif%20Ul%20Islam%2C%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Association%20and%20the%20fact-finding%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201900%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.18.49-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201900%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.18.49-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201900%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.18.49-PM-300x160.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201900%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.18.49-PM-1024x544.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665719%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22638%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EZahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Marhaura.%20Photo%3A%20Saif%20Ul%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20is%20a%20small%20house%2C%20built%20under%20a%20government%20scheme.%20In%20Marhaura%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20faces%20are%20all%20behind%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghoonghat%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Epardah%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20team%20found%20that%20Zahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20sons%20work%20as%20labourers.%20His%20wife%2C%20observing%20the%20Islamic%20mournigng%20period%2C%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Shafaqat%2C%20the%20bone%20mill%20owner%20who%20employed%20Zahiruddin%2C%20conversed%20with%20the%20team.%20Shafaqat%20has%20been%20supporting%20the%20family%20and%20is%20its%20only%20help%20at%20this%20time.%20Zahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20sons%2C%20who%20do%20not%20have%20formal%20education%2C%20also%20appeared%20to%20depend%20heavily%20on%20Shafaqat%2C%20directing%20the%20fact-finding%20team%E2%80%99s%20questions%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShafaqat%20told%20the%20team%20that%20his%20grandfather%20had%20started%20this%20business%20%E2%80%93%20in%201955.%20Since%20then%2C%20his%20have%20been%20running%20it%20smoothly.%20The%20business%20employs%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20both.%20Since%20inception%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20communal%20incident%20that%20any%20of%20its%20workers%20have%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShafaqat%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20that%20those%20who%20killed%20Zahiruddin%20were%20fringe%20elements%20but%20that%20he%20was%20lynched%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20police.%20%E2%80%9CFive%20accused%20in%20mob%20lynching%20have%20pleaded%20guilty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20raging%20mob%20and%20a%20disabled%20target%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESohail%2C%20the%20younger%20brother%20of%20Shafaqat%2C%20also%20works%20at%20the%20bone%20mill.%20Sohail%20said%20that%20on%20June%2028%2C%20five%20employees%20had%20accompanied%20Zahiruddin%20on%20the%20journey%20to%20Marhaura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truck%20driver%20had%20called%20Sohail%20at%20around%20half%20past%20three%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20informing%20him%20that%20the%20side%20wing%20of%20their%20vehicle%20has%20broken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201918%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.11-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201918%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.11-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201918%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.11-PM-300x282.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201918%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.11-PM-1024x961.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665720%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221126%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20vandalised%20vehicle%2C%20after%20Zahiruddin%E2%80%99s%20death.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESohail%20then%20left%20his%20home%20for%20Paigambarpur%20when%20he%20received%20another%20call%20on%20the%20way%20from%20another%20employees.%20From%20him%2C%20Sohail%20learnt%20that%20local%20youth%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20mostly%20military%20aspirants%2C%20who%20are%20coloquially%20called%20%E2%80%9Ctrainees%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20had%20gathered%20around%20the%20vehicle.%20The%20caller%20suspected%20that%20they%20had%20been%20alerted%20by%20the%20smell%20of%20bones.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20inspecting%20the%20vehicle%20by%20climbing%20on%20top%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20caller%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20phones%20were%20then%20snatched.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CKal%20tumhara%20tyohar%20hai.%20Tum%20log%20bahut%20ud%20rahe%20ho.%20Tumhein%20tumhari%20auqat%20dikhate%3C%2Fem%3E%20hai%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20attackers%20had%20allegedly%20told%20the%20bone%20mill%20employees.%20Translated%2C%20the%20line%20means%2C%20%E2%80%9CTomorrow%20is%20your%20festival%2C%20so%20you%20guys%20are%20on%20quite%20a%20high.%20We%20will%20show%20you%20your%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESohail%20stressed%20that%20the%20vehicle%20had%20been%20loaded%20only%20with%20bones%20and%20had%20no%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sohail%20reached%20Paigambarpur%20with%20a%20companion%20on%20his%20Scorpio%2C%20they%20did%20saw%20a%20raging%20mob%20awaiting%20them.%20They%20parked%20the%20vehicle%20behind%20the%20truck%20and%20dismounted.%20It%20was%20around%20sunset%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20mob%20of%2070%20people%20attacked%20us%20with%20stones.%20They%20broke%20the%20glass%20of%20our%20Scorpio%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sohail%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScared%2C%20Sohail%20and%20his%20companion%20got%20on%20the%20car%20and%20drove%20away%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20other%20five%20employees%20also%20ran%20for%20their%20lives.%20Zahiruddin%2C%20who%20had%20been%20partially%20disabled%20since%20childhood%2C%20could%20not%20run.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20could%20not%20withstand%20the%20brick%20blows%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sohail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Unique%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShafaqat%E2%80%99s%20company%20is%20called%20%E2%80%98Unique%20Bone%20Fertilizers%E2%80%99.%20He%20said%20that%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cunique%20business%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20earlier%20a%205%25%20sales%20tax%20applicable%20to%20the%20business%20before%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20was%20introduced.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20GST%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20decided%20to%20promote%20the%20business%20and%20waived%20the%20tax.%20Currently%20it%20is%20nil.%20The%20factory%2C%20licensed%20under%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Employment%20Generation%20Program%20(PMEGP)%2C%20has%20been%20successfully%20running%20for%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20formation%20of%20this%20bone%20factory%20(bone%20mill)%20was%20overseen%20by%20the%20Task%20Force%20Committee%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20who%20also%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20approving%20the%20loan%20for%20the%20PMEGP%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shafaqat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20raw%20material%20%E2%80%93%20cattle%20bones%20%E2%80%93%20collected%20from%20slaughterhouses%20and%20dead%20animals%20found%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20serve%20as%20the%20primary%20source%20for%20our%20operations.%20%E2%80%9COur%20core%20process%20involves%20crushing%20these%20bones%20and%20supplying%20them%20to%20gelatine%20factories.%20The%20gelatine%20produced%20is%20further%20sold%20to%20pharmaceutical%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShafaqat%20manages%20the%20material%20collection%20specifically%20from%20Bihar%2C%20while%20his%20supply%20chain%20extends%20throughout%20India.%20He%20supplies%20to%20renowned%20companies%20like%20Sterling%20Biotech%20and%20India%20Gelatine.%20He%20has%20demanded%20the%20formation%20of%20strict%20laws%20against%20attacks%20on%20employees%20from%20the%20convenor%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Haddi%20Factory%20Union%E2%80%99%2C%20P.D.%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20communal%20incident%20that%20the%20panchayat%20of%20Paigambarpur%20has%20witnessed.%20In%20July%202019%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fthree-lynched-on-suspicion-of-cattle-theft-in-bihars-saran-5837298%2F%5C%22%3Emob%20lynching%3C%2Fa%3E%20killed%20three%20locals%2C%20Bides%20Nat%2C%20Raju%20Nat%2C%20and%20Naushad%20Qureshi.%20The%20mob%20had%20suspected%20them%20of%20cattle%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20told%20the%20fact-finding%20team%20that%20no%20police%20action%20was%20taken%20in%20that%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CZahiruddin%20would%20not%20have%20died%20if%20serious%20action%20was%20taken%20in%20the%20earlier%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690597835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28201937%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-8.19.30-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbihar-partially-disabled-bone-factory-worker-lynched-on-suspicion-of-cattle-theft%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Muslim%20man%20in%20Bihar%20was%20lynched%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20at%20least%2070%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20smuggling%20beef.%20Fifty-five-year-old%20Zahiruddin%20was%20a%20truck%20driver%20who%20worked%20for%20a%20bone%20byproduct%20manufacturing%20factory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbihar-partially-disabled-bone-factory-worker-lynched-on-suspicion-of-cattle-theft%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joe%20Biden%20openly%20acknowledges%207th%20grandchild%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20son%20Hunter%20and%20an%20Arkansas%20woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690597633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102220984%2Cimgsize-18936.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-openly-acknowledges-7th-grandchild-the-daughter-of-son-hunter-and-an-arkansas-woman%2Farticleshow%2F102220930.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102220930.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden%20has%20acknowledged%20his%20seventh%20grandchild%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Hunter%20Biden%2C%20Joe%20Biden's%20son%2C%20fathered%20the%20child%20with%20Lunden%20Roberts%20in%202018.%20As%20part%20of%20a%20statement%2C