ng%20halt%20for%20the%20tribal%20community%20on%20May%203%2C%20when%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20erupted%2C%20which%20killed%20over%20160%20people%20and%20displaced%20around%2070%2C000%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chaos%20led%20to%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20Tribal%20Market%20in%20New%20Lambulane%2C%20putting%20the%20means%20of%20livelihood%20of%20several%20residents%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20shocking%20incident%20on%20July%2025%2C%20where%20around%2035-40%20houses%20belonging%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%20were%20set%20ablaze%2C%20further%20heightened%20fear%20and%20distress%20among%20the%20tribal%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state-imposed%20curfew%20begins%20at%206%20pm%2C%20however%2C%20the%20shops%20in%20New%20Lambulane%20remain%20shuttered%20throughout%20the%20day%20as%20people%20are%20scared%20to%20move%20out%20of%20their%20houses.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20case%20since%20the%20outbreak%20of%20violence.%20The%20families%20find%20themselves%20enclosed%20in%20their%20colonies%20with%20limited%20access%2C%20depending%20on%20police%20intervention%20for%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residents%20are%20overwhelmed%20with%20feelings%20of%20isolation%20and%20despair.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20Kuki%20family%20expressed%20their%20plea%20for%20justice%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20only%20wish%20is%20for%20justice.%20We%20request%20both%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20ensure%20impartial%20justice%20prevails%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20justice%20that%20can%20distinguish%20between%20right%20and%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20families%2C%20particularly%2C%20have%20been%20surviving%20without%20pay%20for%20over%20three%20months%2C%20unable%20to%20venture%20out%20due%20to%20the%20hostile%20environment.%20A%20distressed%20Kuki%20individual%2C%20speaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20community%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20few%20days%2C%20our%20money%20will%20run%20out%2C%20then%20what%20will%20we%20do%2C%20you%20tell%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20families%20declined%20to%20directly%20respond%20to%20questions%20on%20their%20views%20on%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20and%20a%20separate%20state.%20Instead%2C%20they%20said%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%2C%20devout%20elders%20and%20our%20families%20gather%20and%20pray%20together%20at%201%20pm%2C%20seeking%20God%E2%80%99s%20intervention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-after-80-year-old-meitei-woman-burnt-alive-in-her-own-home-family-says-police-yet-to-act%5C%22%3EManipur%3A%20After%2080-Year-Old%20Meitei%20Woman%20Burnt%20Alive%20in%20Her%20Own%20Home%2C%20Family%20Says%20Police%20Yet%20to%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20glimmer%20of%20unity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%2030%20Kuki%20families%20and%20five%20Naga%20families%20currently%20reside%20in%20New%20Lambulane.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20New%20Lambulane%20Baptist%20Church%20remains%20untouched%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20circulating%20news%20about%20all%20churches%20in%20the%20valley%20being%20burnt%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28194126%2Fimage-1181.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22951%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28194126%2Fimage-1181.png%20767w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28194126%2Fimage-1181-300x163.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665713%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22516%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20Lambulane%20Baptist%20Church.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20adversities%2C%20a%20glimmer%20of%20unity%20can%20be%20observed%20in%20the%20New%20Lambulane%20area%2C%20as%20Naga%20and%20Kuki%20families%20stand%20together.%20A%20Naga%20resident%20confidently%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20fight%20between%20brothers%20of%20the%20same%20family%2C%20and%20once%20the%20parents%20%5Breferring%20to%20the%20government%5D%20look%20into%20it%2C%20the%20fight%20will%20either%20cease%20or%20prolong%20indefinitely.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20long%20it%20will%20last.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20questioned%20about%20safety%20concerns%20in%20the%20area%2C%20a%20resident%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20little%20different%20from%20the%20past%20days.%20Whenever%20any%20mob%20came%2C%20they%20would%20not%20see%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20Naga%20or%20Kuki%2C%20and%20anything%20can%20happen%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20asked%20the%20resident%20quoted%20above%20if%20any%20of%20his%20Meitei%20friends%20called%20to%20check%20in%20on%20him%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20strife%2C%20to%20which%20the%20Naga%20individual%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20they%20called%20me.%20They%20asked%20if%20I%20need%20any%20help%2C%20and%20they%20are%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20me%2C%20ready%20to%20provide%20any%20assistance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20appears%20that%20despite%20ongoing%20tensions%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20solidarity%20and%20empathy%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20calls%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20persist%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20emphasise%20their%20desire%20to%20coexist%20as%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20representative%20of%20ITLF%20Ginza%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CPhysically%2C%20we%20are%20separated.%20The%20CM%20is%20only%20the%20CM%20of%20Meiteis.%20The%20Manipur%20Police%20only%20support%20the%20Meiteis.%20%5BWe%20have%20received%5D%20no%20relief%20help%20from%20the%20Manipur%20government.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20separated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftheir-children-missing-and-the-authorities-silent-two-manipuri-families-dont-know-where-to-turn%5C%22%3ETheir%20Children%20Missing%20and%20the%20Authorities%20Silent%2C%20Two%20Manipuri%20Families%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Know%20Where%20to%20Turn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20solace%20in%20prayers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20tensions%20and%20uncertainties%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20New%20Lambulane%20find%20solace%20in%20their%20faith%20and%20prayers%2C%20hoping%20for%20unbiased%20justice%20from%20both%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20we%20want%20is%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20our%20request%20to%20both%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20is%20to%20bring%20justice%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20justice%20without%20being%20biased%2C%20justice%20that%20can%20determine%20who%20is%20right%20and%20who%20is%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20New%20Lambulane%20area%20remains%20complex%20and%20sensitive%2C%20with%20lives%20hanging%20in%20the%20balance%20as%20the%20community%20awaits%20a%20resolution%20to%20their%20predicament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20Imphal%20East%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Shivakanta%20about%20the%20security%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20Manipur%20police%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20Naga-Kuki%20residents%20in%20Imphal.%20He%20said%20four%20companies%20of%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPF)%2C%20besides%20the%20state%20police%2C%20are%20deployed%20for%20guarding%20the%20New%20Checkon%20and%20New%20Lambulane%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20provided%20round%20the%20clock%20security%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20%5BMay%203%5D%20incident%20happened%20in%20Churachandpur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAPF%20was%20deployed%20from%20May%207%20in%20the%20Churachandpur%20district.%20Before%20that%2C%20police%2C%20mostly%20aided%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20or%20the%20army%2C%20were%20present%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20central%20forces%2C%20more%20security%20was%20provided%20to%20the%20affected%20areas%20of%20the%20district%2C%20including%20New%20Checkon%2C%20New%20Lambulane%20area%2C%20and%20peripheral%20areas.%20When%20there%E2%80%99s%20any%20apprehension%20for%20the%20security%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20areas%2C%20the%20police%20are%20always%20there%20to%20assist%20them.%20Be%20it%20someone%20needing%20a%20drop%20at%20the%20airport%20or%20someone%20needing%20to%20take%20out%20their%20important%20documents%20or%20goods%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690594217000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28193956%2Fimage-1180.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsurviving-without-pay-unable-to-venture-out-the-life-of-kuki-families-since-the-manipur-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20it%20is%20being%20said%20that%20no%20one%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20is%20living%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20and%20no%20one%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community%20is%20living%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20the%20ground%20reality%20seems%20different.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsurviving-without-pay-unable-to-venture-out-the-life-of-kuki-families-since-the-manipur-violence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australia%20helicopter%20crash%3A%20Four%20military%20aircrew%20missing%22%