%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fniger-coup-general-abdourahmane-tchiani-declares-himself-new-leader-and-asks-for-support-12929350%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20We%20Know%20So%20Little%20About%20The%20U.S.%20%E2%80%98Union-Busting%E2%80%99%20Industry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Weak%20disclosure%20rules%20have%20helped%20keep%20anti-union%20consulting%20and%20legal%20work%20in%20the%20shadows.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690551969000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F64c291632400001900572ade.jpg%3Fcache%3Dueakpq0a9b%26ops%3D224_126%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fwhy-we-know-so-little-about-the-us-union-busting-industry_n_64c28622e4b03ad2b897077f%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weak%20disclosure%20rules%20have%20helped%20keep%20anti-union%20consulting%20and%20legal%20work%20in%20the%20shadows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A220%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fwhy-we-know-so-little-about-the-us-union-busting-industry_n_64c28622e4b03ad2b897077f%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Do%20Brands%20Manage%20Plastic%20Waste%3F%20Entrepreneur%E2%80%99s%20Credits%20System%20Cuts%2045000%20KG%20From%20Landfills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20remember%20how%20you%20spent%20your%20free%20time%20in%20Class%2012%3F%20Most%20of%20us%20spent%20it%20playing%20sports%20like%20football%2C%20cricket%2C%20or%20badminton%2C%20whereas%20some%20dedicated%20students%20used%20that%20time%20to%20study%20for%20the%20board%20exams.%20But%20not%20Bhagyashree%20Bhansali.%20She%20went%20and%20joined%20the%202011%20anti-corruption%20movement%20launched%20by%20activist%20Anna%20Hazare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20devoted%20her%20college%20life%20to%20addressing%20public%20grievances.%20While%20pursuing%20her%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20business%20administration%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20advis