%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20Bhagyashree%20learnt%20a%20lot%20about%20plastic%20recycling.%20She%20went%20to%20various%20exhibitions%20to%20see%20the%20different%20recycling%20machines%20used%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMachines%20used%20in%20Germany%20and%20China%20would%20segregate%20the%20waste%2C%20but%20those%20machines%20could%20not%20process%20the%20type%20of%20waste%20we%20produced.%20So%20we%20had%20to%20segregate%20and%20clean%20the%20waste%20properly%20before%20using%20the%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2029-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20set%20up%20small%20segregation%20systems%20and%20tweaked%20the%20machinery%20to%20work%20according%20to%20the%20waste%20they%20needed%20to%20recycle%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20college%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20work%20with%20local%20recyclers%20and%20partnered%20with%20organisations%20like%20Mohan%20Meakins%2C%20Whirlpool%2C%20and%20Arvind%20Mills%20to%20establish%20efficient%20in-house%20plastic%20waste%20management%20systems.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20how%20to%20identify%20different%20kinds%20of%20plastic%2C%20its%20nature%2C%20qualities%20and%20recyclability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20these%20learnings%20which%20eventually%20led%20to%20her%20startup%2C%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20(TDC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELove%20for%20skincare%20turned%20into%20a%20business%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201113px)%20100vw%2C%201113px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221113%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plastic%20waste%20being%20processed%20by%20TDC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256.jpeg%201113w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-300x192.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-500x320.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-768x491.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-7-1690546256-150x96.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325576%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPlastic%20waste%20is%20recycled%20by%20TDC%20in%20partnership%20with%20recyclers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202020%2C%20Bhagyashree%20moved%20to%20Rajasthan%20after%20getting%20married.%20In%20Jaipur%2C%20she%20again%20started%20consulting%20with%20the%20government%20on%20ways%20to%20manage%20waste%20better.%20But%20a%20month%20later%2C%20the%20nation%20went%20under%20lockdown.%20COVID%20also%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20deal%20with%20waste%2C%20says%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20with%20the%20local%20pollution%20control%20board%20during%20the%20lockdown.%20With%20the%20addition%20of%20used%20masks%20and%20gloves%2C%20we%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20ways%20to%20segregate%20contaminated%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20also%20saw%20a%20rise%20in%20D2C%20(direct-to-consumer)%20brands%2C%20including%20skincare.%20Newly%20married%2C%20she%20says%20she%20loved%20trying%20on%20different%20skincare%20products.%20But%20while%20others%20focussed%20on%20the%20product%2C%20Bhagyashree%20focused%20on%20the%20packaging!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20I%20see%20a%20new%20brand%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20catches%20my%20eye%20is%20the%20packaging.%20Almost%20100%20new%20brands%20have%20come%20up%2C%20and%20most%20FMCG%20(fast-moving%20consumer%20goods)%20brands%20use%20low-value%20packaging.%20I%20was%20horrified%20at%20the%20waste%20we%20are%20accumulating%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20now%20Mumbai-based%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311038%2Fmani-vajipey-raj-madangopal-banyan-nation-hyderabad-recycle-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-bottles-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20generated%20by%20so%20many%20new%20brands%20with%20new%20types%20of%20packaging%20gave%20her%20sleepless%20nights.%20This%20led%20her%20to%20start%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20in%20November%202020%20to%20%E2%80%9Creduce%20waste%2C%20revive%20lives%20and%20restore%20the%20ecological%20balance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20is%20a%20plastic%20credit%20platform%20that%20helps%20brands%20neutralise%20their%20plastic%20waste.%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqdA8n1ISWi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20(%40thedisposalcompany)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20startups%20to%20do%20this%20in%20India%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20the%20first-mover%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Disposal%20Company%20neutralises%20the%20plastic%20waste%20generated%20by%20a%20brand%20by%20recovering%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20plastic%20from%20landfills%20and%20recycling%20it.%20We%20then%20report%20it%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%2C%20Bhagyashree%20says%20they%20first%20educate%20brands%20on%20how%20to%20improve%20their%20packaging%20and%20eliminate%20plastic%20wherever%20possible.%20They%20work%20with%20design%20labs%20to%20do%20so.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ideal%20thing%20is%20to%20reduce%20plastic.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20brands%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%2C%20or%20their%20products%20can%E2%80%99t%20sustain%20in%20other%20forms%20of%20packaging.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20we%20help%20them%20reduce%20their%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDC%20works%20with%2070%20brands%20across%20India%2C%20Singapore%20and%20the%20UK.%20Its%20clients%20include%20companies%20like%20mCaffeine%2C%20Slurrp%20Farm%2C%20The%20Souled%20Store%2C%20Bombay%20Shaving%20Company%2C%20Blue%20Tokai%20Coffee%2C%20and%20SLAY%20Coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20collaborates%20with%20rag%20pickers%20and%20waste%20segregators%20to%20retrieve%20plastic%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20training%20and%20support%20to%20improve%20waste%20workers%E2%80%99%20skills.%20We%20also%20give%20them%20proper%20safety%20gear.%20We%20have%20provided%20jobs%20to%20500%20such%20waste%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bhagyashree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20TDC%20knows%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20neutralised%2C%20they%20retrieve%20that%20much%20waste%20from%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfills%20with%20the%20help%20of%20rag%20pickers.%20Once%20retrieved%2C%20they%20segregate%20the%20plastic%20and%20send%20it%20to%20recyclers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDC%20works%20with%20recycling%20companies%20like%20Thermowaste%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20recycle%20plastic%20waste%20into%20granules.%20We%20sell%20these%20granules%20to%20companies%20who%20use%20them%20to%20make%20sustainable%20products%20like%20photo%20frames%2C%20toys%20etc.%20Mixed%20plastic%2C%20which%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20recycle%2C%20is%20sent%20to%20a%20plant%20that%20converts%20it%20to%20energy.%20We%20recycle%20about%2060%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20per%20month.%2020%E2%80%9325%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20credit%20is%20given%20to%20TDC%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sanyam%20Jain%20of%20Thermowaste%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20a%20better%20planet%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201196px)%20100vw%2C%201196px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221196%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waste%20being%20picked%20up%20by%20TDC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327.jpeg%201196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-300x167.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-500x278.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-768x427.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-14-min-1690546327-150x83.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325578%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22665%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPlastic%20waste%20is%20picked%20up%20from%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20by%20a%20TDC%20worker%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDC%20helps%20in%20recycling%2045%2C000%20kg%20of%20plastic%20waste%20per%20month.%20The%20journey%20has%20not%20been%20easy%20though%2C%20reflects%20the%20founder.%20It%20took%20her%20seven%20months%20to%20get%20the%20first%20client%20%E2%80%94%20mCaffeine.%20What%20kept%20her%20motivated%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20I%20buy%20a%20milk%20packet%20or%20carton%2C%20I%20think%20about%20the%20microplastics%20in%20it.%20My%20mother%20is%20a%20cancer%20survivor.%20There%20is%20a%20probability%20of%20me%20getting%20cancer%20too.%20Consuming%20microplastics%20can%20further%20add%20to%20our%20woes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBisphenol%20A%20(BPA)%20is%20a%20chemical%20used%20in%20several%20plastic%20products%20and%20packaging.%20An%20%3Cem%3ENCBI%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%20that%20many%20studies%20have%20confirmed%20that%20BPA%20is%20associated%20with%20obesity%2C%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20reproductive%20disorder%2C%20and%20breast%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20think%20of%20having%20a%20child%20in%20the%20future%2C%20these%20thoughts%20worry%20me.%20I%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323368%2Fsonika-bhasin-sustainable-mom-lifestyle-plastic-free-july-composting-bioenzyme-cloth-diaper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleave%20a%20better%20planet%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20our%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThoughts%20like%20these%20keep%20Bhagyashree%2C%20who%20is%20today%20an%20%E2%80%9Cenvironmental%2C%20social%2C%20and%20corporate%20governance%20(ESG)%20consultant%E2%80%9D%2C%20going.%20She%20urges%20not%20just%20businesses%20but%20everyone%20to%20think%20about%20what%20they%20are%20consuming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20conscious%20consumerism.%20Ask%20the%20brands%20you%20buy%20from%20about%20what%20they%20are%20doing%20for%20the%20environment.%20Hold%20them%20accountable%20and%20they%20will%20start%20taking%20action.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20you%20also%20take%20small%20steps%20in%20your%20daily%20life%20to%20reduce%20plastic%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7068600%2F%23B30-ijerph-17-01212%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENCBI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fwaste-processing-at-ghazipur-landfill-yet-to-pick-up-pace%2Farticle66785760.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Waste%20processing%20at%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20yet%20to%20pick%20up%20pace%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Muneef%20Khan%20for%20The%20Hindu%2C%20Published%20on%2001%20May%202023%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690551389000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325564%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai-based%20Bhagyashree%20Bhansali%20started%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20to%20help%20brands%20neutralise%20their%20plastic%20waste%20by%20recycling%20an%20equal%20amount.%20It%20works%20with%20rag%20pickers%20and%20waste%20segregators%20in%20Delhi%20who%20retrieve%20plastic%20waste%20from%20Ghazipur%20landfills.%22%2C%22