%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20also%20put%20forth%20the%20argument%20that%20considering%20the%20notice%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-congress-no-confidence-modi-speaker%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eno-confidence%20motion%20had%20already%20been%20accepted%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20no%20other%20business%20should%20be%20conducted%20till%20the%20motion%20is%20discussed%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELeader%20of%20Congress%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20said%20that%20in%20May%201978%2C%20when%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20moved%2C%20a%20discussion%20was%20held%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20same%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20in%20response%20said%20that%20he%20will%20give%20a%20date%20for%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20and%20asked%20the%20opposition%20members%20to%20allow%20the%20Question%20Hour%20to%20continue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rules%20state%20that%20we%20have%2010%20days%E2%80%99%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Minister%20of%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%2C%20Pralhad%20Joshi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20you%20(Speaker)%20decide%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20for%20the%20discussion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBirla%20then%20adjourned%20the%20session%20till%20noon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20house%20reconvened%20at%20noon%2C%20Rajendra%20Agarwal%20took%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20chair%20and%20began%20the%20session%E2%80%99s%20proceedings%20as%20opposition%20members%20continued%20to%20raise%20slogans%20saying%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cpradhan%20mantri%20jawab%20do%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(p%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erime%20minister%2C%20answer)%2C%E2%80%9D%20holding%20banners%20that%20read%20%E2%80%9CSave%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%2012.07%20pm%2C%20the%20Minister%20for%20Education%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20introduced%20The%20Indian%20Institutes%20of%20Management%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%20This%20Bill%20was%20not%20passed%20and%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20next%20week%20for%20consideration%20and%20passing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Amendment%20Bill%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%2012.09%20pm%2C%20The%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%202023%20was%20taken%20up%20for%20consideration%20and%20passed%20as%20opposition%20members%20were%20seen%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20chair%20holding%20banners%20on%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20amends%20the%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Act%2C%201957.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fbilltrack%2Fthe-mines-and-minerals-development-and-regulation-amendment-bill-2023%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20summary%20of%20the%20Bill%20by%20PRS%20Legislative%20Research%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20while%20the%20earlier%20Act%20prohibited%20pitting%2C%20trenching%2C%20drilling%2C%20and%20sub-surface%20excavation%20as%20part%20of%20reconnaissance%20%E2%80%93%20the%20new%20Bill%20allows%20these%20prohibited%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20introduces%20an%20exploration%20licence%2C%20which%20will%20authorise%20either%20reconnaissance%20or%20prospecting%2C%20or%20both%20activities%20for%20specified%20minerals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20exploration%20licence%20will%20be%20issued%20for%2029%20minerals%20specified%20in%20the%20Seventh%20Schedule.%20These%20include%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20copper%2C%20cobalt%2C%20nickel%2C%20lead%2C%20potash%2C%20and%20rock%20phosphate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20exploration%20licence%20will%20be%20granted%20by%20the%20state%20government%20through%20competitive%20bidding%20but%20the%20Union%20government%20will%20prescribe%20details%20such%20as%20manner%20of%20auction%2C%20terms%20and%20conditions%2C%20and%20bidding%20parameters%20for%20exploration%20licence%20through%20rules.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20under%20the%20earlier%20Act%20auction%20of%20concessions%20was%20undertaken%20by%20the%20state%20governments%2C%20except%20in%20certain%20specified%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20the%20amended%20Bill%20adds%20that%20auction%20for%20composite%20licence%20and%20mining%20lease%20for%20specified%20critical%20and%20strategic%20minerals%20will%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20central%20government.%C2%A0%20These%20minerals%20include%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20nickel%2C%20phosphate%2C%20potash%2C%20tin%2C%20phosphate%2C%20and%20potash.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20exploration%20licence%20would%20facilitate%2C%20encourage%20and%20incentivize%20private%20sector%20participation%20in%20all%20spheres%20of%20mineral%20exploration%20for%20critical%20and%20deep-seated%20minerals%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbills_acts%2Fbills_parliament%2F2023%2FMines%2520and%2520Minerals%2520(Development%2520and%2520Regulation)%2520Amendment%2520Bill%2C%25202023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esays%20the%20Bill%E2%80%99s%20statement%20of%20objects%20and%20reasons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20bill%20was%20introduced%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20coals%20and%20mines%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20(who%20also%20has%20the%20parliamentary%20affairs%20portfolio)%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20N.K.%20Premachandran%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Socialist%20Party%20had%20said%20that%20it%20is%20against%20the%20principle%20of%20federalism%20and%20will%20benefit%20multinational%20corporations%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenergy.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fcoal%2Fmines-and-minerals-development-and-regulation-amendment-bill-2023-introduced-in-lok-sabha%2F102139537%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20two%20MPs%20spoke%20during%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20Bill%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Singh%20BJP%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20amendment%20will%20allow%20India%20to%20become%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ea%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Etmarnirbhar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20word%20for%20%E2%80%98self%20reliant%E2%80%99%20and%20often%20a%20catchphrase%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20%E2%80%93%20and%20allow%20India%20to%20strengthen%20its%20position%20in%20the%20global%20market%20and%20remove%20bureaucratic%20hurdles%20to%20gain%20licences%20and%20help%20mining%20companies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20MP%20M%20Srinivas%20Reddy%20was%20then%20asked%20to%20speak%20as%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20seen%20raising%20copies%20of%20the%20constitution%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20chair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%2012.15%20pm%2C%20minister%20Joshi%20gave%20his%20closing%20statement%2C%20calling%20the%20bill%20%E2%80%9Crevolutionary%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20visible%20change%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy%20because%20of%20our%20policies%20and%20we%20have%20become%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20of%20the%20world%20under%20Modi.%20With%20a%20clear%20vision%20and%20mind%20we%20are%20bringing%20changes%20that%20will%20benefit%20the%20nation%20not%20dynasties.%20Their%20(opposition)%20MP%20has%20even%20been%20jailed%20for%20coal%20allocation%20corruption%2C%E2