ining%2C%20and%20building%20the%20ecosystem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20raise%20awareness%20among%20low-income%20women%20through%20campaigns.%20Then%2C%20we%20train%20women%20with%20the%20help%20of%20our%20women%20instructors.%20We%20are%20also%20focused%20on%20institutionalising%20the%20concept%20of%20mobility%20so%20that%20these%20women%20enter%20into%20the%20workforce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharati%20says%20that%20her%20team%20does%20not%20stop%20at%20training%20women%2C%20they%20are%20also%20helping%20women%20get%20jobs.%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20we%20teach%20women%20how%20to%20drive%20not%20with%20a%20focus%20that%20they%20have%20to%20become%20drivers%2C%20but%20with%20a%20focus%20that%20she%20learns%20it%20as%20a%20skill%20and%20then%20access%20opportunities%20as%20per%20their%20wish%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20Bharathi%20faces%20in%20training%20women%20to%20drive%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20not%20confident%20taking%20vehicles%20on%20the%20road.%20Compared%20to%20men%2C%20they%20are%20subconsciously%20raised%20with%20fear%20in%20mind%20in%20terms%20of%20driving.%20We%20invest%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20helping%20them%20to%20overcome%20their%20fear%2C%20because%20learning%20to%20drive%20is%20the%20easiest%20thing.%20All%20of%20our%20women%20were%20able%20to%20learn%20to%20drive%20within%2015-20%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FMOWO-2-1690464073.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bharati%20says%20that%20her%20team%20does%20not%20stop%20at%20training%20women%2C%20they%20are%20also%20helping%20women%20get%20jobs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FMO