%2F2023%2F07%2FTarini-malhotra-4-1690465245-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FTarini-malhotra-4-1690465245-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FTarini-malhotra-4-1690465245-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FTarini-malhotra-4-1690465245-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20has%20also%20helped%2021%20artists%20sell%20their%20work%20online%20and%20in%20onsite%20exhibitions.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Tarini%20Malhotra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Preet%20Singh%2C%20the%20team%20lead%20and%20manager%20of%20the%20company%20who%20trained%20Aditya%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20joined%2C%20I%20was%20very%20nervous%20and%20a%20little%20unsure%20of%20how%20he%20would%20fit%20in%20here.%20But%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20it%20was%20not%20so%20difficult%20to%20incubate%20him.%20Aditya%20is%20a%20hardworking%20individual%20and%20was%20able%20to%20adapt%20to%20everything%20at%20a%20good%20pace%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20even%20extended%20his%20internship%20and%20gave%20him%20extra%20benefits.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20great%20initiative%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20seeing%20more%20inclusivity%20at%20workplaces%20all%20across%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20she%20comes%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20neurodivergent%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20neurodivergent%20community%20is%20quite%20close-knit%20and%20always%20in%20touch.%20Most%20times%2C%20people%20hear%20about%20us%20from%20someone%20and%20show%20up%20on%20their%20own%20looking%20for%20work.%20If%20we%20are%20not%20approached%2C%20then%20we%20also%20have%20tie-ins%20with%20six%20other%20NGOs%20in%20and%20around%20Delhi%20NCR%20region%20who%20help%20us%20reach%20the%20remotest%20person%20who%20may%20need%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20my%20parents%20and%20teachers%20have%20motivated%20me%20to%20find%20solutions%20to%20societal%20problems.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20understood%20that%20regardless%20of%20my%20chosen%20career%2C%20improving%20society%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F165682%2Famazon-india-inclusive-workplace-hearing-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eensuring%20inclusivity%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewill%20remain%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tarini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20for%20the%20future%2C%20we%20want%20to%20help%20neurodivergent%20entrepreneurs%20get%20funding%20and%20help%20them%20boost%20their%20ventures.%20This%20will%20not%20only%20uplift%20them%20but%20also%20uplift%20the%20people%20of%20their%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20volunteer%20with%20Tarini%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20her%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaisubah.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enaisubah.org.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690466088000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FTarini-malhotra-3-1690465096.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Diana%20Award-recipient%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Tarini%20Malhotra%20(18)%20started%20Nai%20Subah%20Foundation%20when%20she%20was%20just%2016%20to%20help%20people%20with%20neurodiversity%20get%20jobs.%20She%20has%20helped%20over%2050%20people%20secure%20jobs%20and%20raised%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20neurodivergent%20artists%20by%20showcasing%20their%20artwork.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22eng