sterious-men-showed-up_n_64b7dd60e4b0dcb4cab68347%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20Pet%20Can%20Eat%20My%20Plate%E2%80%99%3A%20Brothers%20Use%20Waste%20From%20Rice%20Farming%20to%20Make%20Tableware%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPaddling%20up%20to%20the%20wave%20on%20Kovalam%20Beach%20in%20Kerala%20every%20Sunday%20helped%20Rishabh%20Suri%20find%20the%20motivation%20to%20improve%20his%20sport.%20However%2C%20as%20he%20enjoyed%20surfing%2C%20he%20found%20himself%20in%20a%20weird%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSurfing%20is%20already%20a%20difficult%20sport.%20While%20practising%2C%20often%2C%20a%20paper%20or%20plastic%20cup%20would%20hit%20my%20head%20and%20sometimes%20a%20plastic%20bag%20would%20get%20wrapped%20around%20my%20feet.%20The%20sea%20is%20full%20of%20it!%20When%20you%20go%20slightly%20outward%20into%20the%20sea%2C%20huge%20amounts%20of%20plastic%20lie%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2026-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20another%20such%20incident%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202018%2C%20when%20my%20brother%20and%20I%20were%20trekking%20to%20spot%20gorillas%20in%20Uganda%20mountains%2C%20we%20spotted%20plastic%20there%20too!%20We%20realised%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20plastic%20even%20in%20the%20remotest%20places.%20Since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20been%20my%20quest%20to%20work%20on%20something%20that%20solves%20an%20environmental%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20do%20their%20bit%20to%20tackle%20the%20growing%20plastic%20problem%2C%20siblings%20Rishabh%20and%20Rohan%20started%20Qudrat%2C%20a%20Kerala-based%20startup%20that%20creates%20biodegradable%20tableware%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277852%2Fthoosan-edible-plates-spoons-tableware-from-kerala-biodegradable-wheat-rice%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E