ays%2C%20they%20sold%20about%2025%2C000%20units%20of%20plates%2C%20straws%2C%20spoons%2C%20and%20cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20quest%20to%20find%20a%20better%20substitute%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20after%20dropping%20out%20of%20Chartered%20Accountancy%2C%20he%20got%20into%20his%20family%20business%20of%20selling%20motorcycles.%20The%20BCom%20graduate%20continued%20the%20automobile%20franchise%20business%20till%202020%20before%20founding%20his%20own%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22They%20collect%20husk%20and%20rice%20grain%20from%20mills%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20and%20straw%20from%20farmers%20across%20Kerala%20belt%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fqudrat-1690203332-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324928%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThey%20collect%20husk%20and%20rice%20grain%20from%20mills%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20and%20straw%20from%20farmers%20across%20the%20Kerala%20belt.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pandemic%20gave%20us%20an%20opportunity%20to%20research%20how%20agricultural%20waste%20could%20be%20converted%20into%20disposable%20tableware.%20We%20