%20ultrasound%20and%20MRI%20imaging.%20Similarly%2C%20when%20there%20are%20gas%20leaks%20or%20crop%20diseases%2C%20normal%20satellites%20cannot%20see%20what%E2%80%99s%20wrong.%20This%20is%20where%20hyperspectral%20imaging%20satellites%20come%20in.%20They%20can%20capture%20images%20in%20over%20a%20hundred%20wavelengths%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Awais.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombined%20with%20analytical%20tools%2C%20this%20data%20can%20be%20used%20to%20find%20out%20information%20about%20agriculture%2C%20mining%2C%20the%20environment%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%9CSimilar%20to%20how%20sensors%20in%20a%20hospital%20monitor%20our%20vital%20signs%20like%20heart%20rate%20and%20blood%20pressure%2C%20satellites%20can%20observe%20various%20aspects%20of%20our%20environment.%20They%20can%20detect%20the%20amount%20of%20pollutants%20in%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20measure%20water%20pollution%2C%20identify%20gas%20leaks%2C%20and%20assess%20the%20health%20of%20our%20forests%20and%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20space%20enthusiast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Pixxel%20notes%20on%20their%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9CIdentifying%20these%20resources%20will%20be%20the%20precursor%20to%20building%20infrastructure%20in%20space%20that%20will%20shift%20heavy%20industry%20away%20from%20earth.%20Thereby%20giving%20us%20a%20realistic%20shot%20at%20reclaiming%20our%20planet%20from%20the%20irreversible%20effects%20of%20climate%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPixxel%20monitors%20the%20%E2%80%98pulse%20of%20the%20planet%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201059px)%20100vw%2C%201059px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel1-1689934902.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221059%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20captured%20by%20Pixxel's%20satellite%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpixxel1-1689